es New Roman&quot;&gt;I believe, and I am absolutely certain, and therefore &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background: yellow none repeat scroll 0% 0%; font-size: 12pt; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial&quot;&gt;I believe, that painting is a religious occupation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;, &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;that the actual impulse comes from without, from &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;something else that we do not know, an indefinable &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;power which comes or does not come and which guides &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;your hand &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;People used to say in earlier times that it was the &lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times 