object(text,'1.1.1.3','ON THE DELAY MECHANISM, PROTECTIVE LAYERS, SUPERFICIAL ENEMIES AND THE PREJUDICE TRAP OR THE POSITIVE LONG-TERM EFFECT OF THE NEGATIVE ASSESSMENT OF THE POSITIVE',[
id-60,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-60,
txt-'1.1.1.3',
text_type-'',
