text_title_en-'LETTER TO J. J. ABERBACH',
text_title_ge-'BRIEF AN J. J. ABERBACH',
text_keywords-'Aberbach, vegetative painting, peace treaty with nature, cemetary, New Zealand, Flag for New Zealand, Architecture doctor, Hundertwasser-House, Masterschool, Academy of Fine Arts, Publicity; vegetative Malerei, Friedensvertrag mit der Natur, Friedhof, Neuseeland, Fahne f&uuml;r Neuseeland, Architekturdoktor, Hundertwasser-Haus, Meisterschule, Akademie der bildenden K&uuml;nste, &Ouml;ffentlichkeit',
text_date-'1984-06-23',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;for three months I have been back in my paradise, where the trees, which I planted, have already become forests in which one can walk. I am working on four paintings, which testify even more intensely to my vegetative way of painting.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is this, which distinguishes me from other painters. I do not paint expressive or imitative as has become fashionable today &mdash; still fashionable, but vegetative &mdash; a way of expression of the future ecological (sic!) age, which is beginning now. This will be understood only in ten years or after one generation. For now, one judges my paintings according to their optical appearance as though they were expressive-imitative, and not according their actual content, which has emerged authentically, creatively, organically, vegetatively, magically. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am of good cheer, because I know about my importance as a signpost to a peace treaty with nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One of the most important points regarding the peace treaty with nature is the reunion of the creation of nature and the creation of man, which has been separated for centuries (for instance in the notion Natural History Museum versus Art Historical Museum).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Art must form a bridge to nature and not become even more artificial, i.e. distance itself even more from true Creation. If the art-forming process is already infringing upon the laws of self-creative nature, the result cannot be a work of art in the sense of Creation. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If the building blocks are wrong, no good building can originate.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This process of creative becoming and responsible evolution is very slow and in its beginning stage seemingly inconspicuous like a very young tree. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am also trying to consequently reconcile my painting and my life, my works and my activities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is interesting what Julien Alvard wrote in 1954 in Paris on the occasion of my exhibition at Facchetti: Il faut beaucoup de s&eacute;rieux pour mener &agrave; bien l&rsquo;ironie d&rsquo;une telle entreprise. Et beaucoup de sens moral pour l&rsquo;appr&eacute;cier. Mais ce s&eacute;rieux lui sera compt&eacute; pour folie, cette folie pour calcul, ce calcul pour pr&eacute;m&eacute;ditation. C&rsquo;est tout &agrave; son honneur... [It requires a great seriousness to transform the irony of such an enterprise into virtue, and a vigorous moral sincerity to be able to appreciate it. But his seriousness was interpreted as craziness, the craziness as expediency, and the expediency as premeditated&hellip;]&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am a happy man, because all my activities are focused on one goal and reconciled there.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;1. Painting&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Here I am working on four paintings: &lt;em&gt;Point de vue chinois&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Immigration of an Amphibian Car&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Veena&lt;/em&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Cyclone in Tahiti&lt;/em&gt;), &lt;em&gt;Das Autokreuz&lt;/em&gt; [The Car Cross] (which is a further development of &lt;em&gt;The Crucified of the Road&lt;/em&gt;). At the same time on three Japanese woodcuts in close collaboration with Japanese masters in Kyoto and Tokyo: &lt;em&gt;H&uuml;te tragen Tennos&lt;/em&gt; [Tennos Fly with Hats], &lt;em&gt;Automobil im Regen &lt;/em&gt;[Automobile in the Rain], &lt;em&gt;Das Ende der Wasser &lt;/em&gt;[The End of the Waters]. The Japanese cut the woodblocks according to my instructions.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;But my big bomb I let explode before my departure from Venice: I succeeded to produce with silk screen printing an edition of 10,002 sheets, of which each sheet is different than the other!!! &ldquo;Homo Humus How Do You Do 860 10002 Nights.&rdquo; The sheets of this edition are as unique as the leaves of a tree. An edition, comprising unique copies. &bdquo;A victory of man over chain production, using the reproductive machine to produce creative individuality. A big step towards the liberation of mankind from the worst enslavement in history: the machine made terror.&rdquo; I include a brochure.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;2.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I have won an unbelievable victory in New Zealand. I have succeeded in receiving permission from the N.Z. government to be buried on my land. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This is a first concrete step towards a revolution in the context of the peace treaty with nature and a first acknowledgement. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The cemeteries of the future will be &ldquo;Nature reserves&rdquo;, without walls. The dead will be buried only as deep as the trees planted on the graves can profit from the deceased. The dead do not die, but continue to live on in the form of trees. An actual rebirth, a veritable resurrection takes place.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cemeteries will turn into forests of life. Today, however, burial is a sacrilege against ecology, against life, against the circular flow, against rebirth, against the cosmic laws of nature. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Today, a wedge, a concrete wall is placed between death and life. A four-meter grave so that no root can reach in, hermetically sealed caskets, in which the remains do nothing but rot instead of providing nourishment for life. The natural vegetation on the grave itself is violated by lawn, plastic flowers, concrete covers.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In my &ldquo;cemetery&rdquo; nature can grow as it pleases. Even dying trees are not removed, but abandoned to God&rsquo;s will until the falling branches and stems have turned to humus, giving new life a foundation. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Such a cemetery is a piece of virgin forest. A piece of nature we return. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A piece of territory which man has illegally occupied is given back to nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;3.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I have designed a flag for New Zealand. Attached I am sending a photocopy of the first draft. I already have the support of several secretaries and important personalities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;New Zealand is already searching for a new symbol. I know it will be a great, interesting battle. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This flag, too, is part of the &ldquo;peace treaty with nature.&rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;4.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;My activity as an &ldquo;architecture doctor&rdquo; is presently reaching a first climax in Vienna. On July 9&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; the topping-out ceremony for the &ldquo;Hundertwasser House&rdquo; in the L&ouml;wengasse takes place. After a five-year battle I have succeeded in constructing a house for fifty families, which completely turns its back at the &ldquo;Bauhaus mentality&rdquo;. The inhabitants&rsquo; &ldquo;window right&rdquo; is instituted for the first time! As an advance to the window right all windows have a different size and have been installed in different places, not like soldiers directly one above the other or side by side. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The walls are not machine-smooth, but have been formed rather irregularly by hand. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;On all roofs grow trees and grass. Three tree-tenants grow from three windows. The house attains a romantic character through onion towers and mosaic inlays, which I designed. Each apartment is different from the others; this is recognizable on the exterior walls. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The skyline is not geometrically straight. There is a large hall which is designed as a winter garden, a pedestrian mall and much more. The house is also part of the peace treaty with nature: a &ldquo;house in harmony with nature and man&rdquo;. I am including a flyer of the Community of Vienna.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;5.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;My activities as the head of a master school at the Academy of Fine Arts in Vienna have proved a really great success. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Already now, it is the best school in the Academy. Whole delegations, school classes, visitors from everywhere arrive in order to visit it. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the beginning there were scandals because I had to take over a school, firing students and people who considered the Academy a shelter for the creatively disabled, who hung around the school only because they had paid tuition fees; also because I transformed the school into a forest.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Just imagine: The head of the &ldquo;Master School Hundertwasser&rdquo; is almost always absent, passing the lecture activities to trees and plants, which he brought from the Palm House and installed in the school. &lt;u&gt;My absence creates my presence!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;And the calculation works out. Seven excellent masters have educated themselves in this atmosphere steeped with creativity where even the oxygen-enriched air is by far better than in the other painting classes:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Karin K&ouml;ppl fairytale world&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Markus Schiller a young visionary&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Christian Rausch a new Schiele, however quite different&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Bruno Richard a true na&iuml;ve, a Frenchman&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Anna Stangl animated landscapes&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Martina Hanadou narrative painting reminiscent of hieroglyphic writing&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Maria Trummer a very young realist&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;None of them&lt;/u&gt; imitates Hundertwasser or anybody else! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;An unbelievable victory through a completely new teaching method.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I will later send reproductions united in a calendar!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Apart from the giant trees my school also contains two plant-water purification plants. These are water plants arranged in cascades on top of each that purify the sewage water, rippling gently like a brook while the water passes through them, resulting in half an hour &ldquo;Bach music&rdquo; [Bach = brook; notice the subtle pun!].&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Furthermore I have established within my teaching position a chair entitled &ldquo;Nature &mdash; Art &mdash;Creation&rdquo; where renowned scientists, Nobel Prize Winners contribute their views on the topic of the reunification of art and nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear friend Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;You see why I can be actually content with and proud of myself. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am always glad if that, which is interpreted by others in regard to me as &ldquo;publicity activity&rdquo;, eventually prove as very, very serious, in fact pioneer activities necessary for the future, and when I succeed to create ever new activities almost always discredited as dishonourable or even profit-oriented schemings.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear friend Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am happy to communicate to you as almost the only person a detailed survey of my latest activities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am glad that we have remained friends for so many years. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Please do not forget to send me an exact list of the paintings that were transferred from the Aberbach Collection to other collections, including detailed information on the new owners and their addresses. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;You know how much I am psychically connected with my works, which I consider my children. This was also a condition when I parted from my paintings. Please in the interest of our long and future friendship!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Have paintings of mine been damaged or destroyed during the fire in your brother&rsquo;s house in Paris?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The night has fallen in the Kaurinui valley.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The new flags flow on three flag poles.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cordially yours&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Greetings to your wife and your children.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;for three months I have been back in my paradise, where the trees, which I planted, have already become forests in which one can walk. I am working on four paintings, which testify even more intensely to my vegetative way of painting.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is this, which distinguishes me from other painters. I do not paint expressive or imitative as has become fashionable today &mdash; still fashionable, but vegetative &mdash; a way of expression of the future ecological (sic!) age, which is beginning now. This will be understood only in ten years or after one generation. For now, one judges my paintings according to their optical appearance as though they were expressive-imitative, and not according their actual content, which has emerged authentically, creatively, organically, vegetatively, magically. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am of good cheer, because I know about my importance as a signpost to a peace treaty with nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One of the most important points regarding the peace treaty with nature is the reunion of the creation of nature and the creation of man, which has been separated for centuries (for instance in the notion Natural History Museum versus Art Historical Museum).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Art must form a bridge to nature and not become even more artificial, i.e. distance itself even more from true Creation. If the art-forming process is already infringing upon the laws of self-creative nature, the result cannot be a work of art in the sense of Creation. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If the building blocks are wrong, no good building can originate.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This process of creative becoming and responsible evolution is very slow and in its beginning stage seemingly inconspicuous like a very young tree. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am also trying to consequently reconcile my painting and my life, my works and my activities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is interesting what Julien Alvard wrote in 1954 in Paris on the occasion of my exhibition at Facchetti: Il faut beaucoup de s&eacute;rieux pour mener &agrave; bien l&rsquo;ironie d&rsquo;une telle entreprise. Et beaucoup de sens moral pour l&rsquo;appr&eacute;cier. Mais ce s&eacute;rieux lui sera compt&eacute; pour folie, cette folie pour calcul, ce calcul pour pr&eacute;m&eacute;ditation. C&rsquo;est tout &agrave; son honneur... [It requires a great seriousness to transform the irony of such an enterprise into virtue, and a vigorous moral sincerity to be able to appreciate it. But his seriousness was interpreted as craziness, the craziness as expediency, and the expediency as premeditated&hellip;]&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am a happy man, because all my activities are focused on one goal and reconciled there.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;1. Painting&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Here I am working on four paintings: &lt;em&gt;Point de vue chinois&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Immigration of an Amphibian Car&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Veena&lt;/em&gt; (&lt;em&gt;Cyclone in Tahiti&lt;/em&gt;), &lt;em&gt;Das Autokreuz&lt;/em&gt; [The Car Cross] (which is a further development of &lt;em&gt;The Crucified of the Road&lt;/em&gt;). At the same time on three Japanese woodcuts in close collaboration with Japanese masters in Kyoto and Tokyo: &lt;em&gt;H&uuml;te tragen Tennos&lt;/em&gt; [Tennos Fly with Hats], &lt;em&gt;Automobil im Regen &lt;/em&gt;[Automobile in the Rain], &lt;em&gt;Das Ende der Wasser &lt;/em&gt;[The End of the Waters]. The Japanese cut the woodblocks according to my instructions.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;But my big bomb I let explode before my departure from Venice: I succeeded to produce with silk screen printing an edition of 10,002 sheets, of which each sheet is different than the other!!! &ldquo;Homo Humus How Do You Do 860 10002 Nights.&rdquo; The sheets of this edition are as unique as the leaves of a tree. An edition, comprising unique copies. &bdquo;A victory of man over chain production, using the reproductive machine to produce creative individuality. A big step towards the liberation of mankind from the worst enslavement in history: the machine made terror.&rdquo; I include a brochure.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;2.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I have won an unbelievable victory in New Zealand. I have succeeded in receiving permission from the N.Z. government to be buried on my land. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This is a first concrete step towards a revolution in the context of the peace treaty with nature and a first acknowledgement. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The cemeteries of the future will be &ldquo;Nature reserves&rdquo;, without walls. The dead will be buried only as deep as the trees planted on the graves can profit from the deceased. The dead do not die, but continue to live on in the form of trees. An actual rebirth, a veritable resurrection takes place.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cemeteries will turn into forests of life. Today, however, burial is a sacrilege against ecology, against life, against the circular flow, against rebirth, against the cosmic laws of nature. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Today, a wedge, a concrete wall is placed between death and life. A four-meter grave so that no root can reach in, hermetically sealed caskets, in which the remains do nothing but rot instead of providing nourishment for life. The natural vegetation on the grave itself is violated by lawn, plastic flowers, concrete covers.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In my &ldquo;cemetery&rdquo; nature can grow as it pleases. Even dying trees are not removed, but abandoned to God&rsquo;s will until the falling branches and stems have turned to humus, giving new life a foundation. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Such a cemetery is a piece of virgin forest. A piece of nature we return. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A piece of territory which man has illegally occupied is given back to nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;3.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I have designed a flag for New Zealand. Attached I am sending a photocopy of the first draft. I already have the support of several secretaries and important personalities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;New Zealand is already searching for a new symbol. I know it will be a great, interesting battle. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This flag, too, is part of the &ldquo;peace treaty with nature.&rdquo;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;4.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;My activity as an &ldquo;architecture doctor&rdquo; is presently reaching a first climax in Vienna. On July 9&lt;sup&gt;th&lt;/sup&gt; the topping-out ceremony for the &ldquo;Hundertwasser House&rdquo; in the L&ouml;wengasse takes place. After a five-year battle I have succeeded in constructing a house for fifty families, which completely turns its back at the &ldquo;Bauhaus mentality&rdquo;. The inhabitants&rsquo; &ldquo;window right&rdquo; is instituted for the first time! As an advance to the window right all windows have a different size and have been installed in different places, not like soldiers directly one above the other or side by side. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The walls are not machine-smooth, but have been formed rather irregularly by hand. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;On all roofs grow trees and grass. Three tree-tenants grow from three windows. The house attains a romantic character through onion towers and mosaic inlays, which I designed. Each apartment is different from the others; this is recognizable on the exterior walls. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The skyline is not geometrically straight. There is a large hall which is designed as a winter garden, a pedestrian mall and much more. The house is also part of the peace treaty with nature: a &ldquo;house in harmony with nature and man&rdquo;. I am including a flyer of the Community of Vienna.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;5.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;My activities as the head of a master school at the Academy of Fine Arts in Vienna have proved a really great success. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Already now, it is the best school in the Academy. Whole delegations, school classes, visitors from everywhere arrive in order to visit it. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the beginning there were scandals because I had to take over a school, firing students and people who considered the Academy a shelter for the creatively disabled, who hung around the school only because they had paid tuition fees; also because I transformed the school into a forest.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Just imagine: The head of the &ldquo;Master School Hundertwasser&rdquo; is almost always absent, passing the lecture activities to trees and plants, which he brought from the Palm House and installed in the school. &lt;u&gt;My absence creates my presence!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;And the calculation works out. Seven excellent masters have educated themselves in this atmosphere steeped with creativity where even the oxygen-enriched air is by far better than in the other painting classes:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Karin K&ouml;ppl fairytale world&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Markus Schiller a young visionary&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Christian Rausch a new Schiele, however quite different&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Bruno Richard a true na&iuml;ve, a Frenchman&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Anna Stangl animated landscapes&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Martina Hanadou narrative painting reminiscent of hieroglyphic writing&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Maria Trummer a very young realist&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;None of them&lt;/u&gt; imitates Hundertwasser or anybody else! &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;An unbelievable victory through a completely new teaching method.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I will later send reproductions united in a calendar!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Apart from the giant trees my school also contains two plant-water purification plants. These are water plants arranged in cascades on top of each that purify the sewage water, rippling gently like a brook while the water passes through them, resulting in half an hour &ldquo;Bach music&rdquo; [Bach = brook; notice the subtle pun!].&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Furthermore I have established within my teaching position a chair entitled &ldquo;Nature &mdash; Art &mdash;Creation&rdquo; where renowned scientists, Nobel Prize Winners contribute their views on the topic of the reunification of art and nature.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear friend Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;You see why I can be actually content with and proud of myself. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am always glad if that, which is interpreted by others in regard to me as &ldquo;publicity activity&rdquo;, eventually prove as very, very serious, in fact pioneer activities necessary for the future, and when I succeed to create ever new activities almost always discredited as dishonourable or even profit-oriented schemings.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Dear friend Aberbach,&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am happy to communicate to you as almost the only person a detailed survey of my latest activities. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am glad that we have remained friends for so many years. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Please do not forget to send me an exact list of the paintings that were transferred from the Aberbach Collection to other collections, including detailed information on the new owners and their addresses. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;You know how much I am psychically connected with my works, which I consider my children. This was also a condition when I parted from my paintings. Please in the interest of our long and future friendship!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Have paintings of mine been damaged or destroyed during the fire in your brother&rsquo;s house in Paris?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The night has fallen in the Kaurinui valley.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The new flags flow on three flag poles.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cordially yours&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Greetings to your wife and your children.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Lieber Aberbach,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;bin seit 3 Monaten wieder in meinem Paradies, wo die B&auml;ume, von mir gepflanzt, bereits W&auml;lder geworden sind, in denen man spazieren gehen kann. Ich male an 4 Bildern, die noch intensiver als je zuvor meine vegetative Malweise unter Beweis stellen.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Das ist es eben, was mich von anderen Malern unterscheidet. Ich male nicht expressiv und nicht imitativ so wie es heute Mode - noch - Mode ist, sondern vegetativ, eine Ausdrucksweise der Zukunft des ecologischen (sic!) Zeitalters, das jetzt anbricht. Man wird dies erst nach 10 Jahren oder nach einer Generation verstehen. Vorerst beurteilt man meine Bilder nach dem optischen Schein, so als w&auml;ren sie expressiv-imitativ und nicht nach tats&auml;chlichem Gehalt, der authentisch, sch&ouml;pferisch, organisch, vegetativ, magisch entstanden ist. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich bin aber guten Mutes, denn ich wei&szlig; um meine Bedeutung als Wegweiser zu einem Friedenspakt mit der Natur.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;In diesem Friedenspakt mit der Natur ist einer der wichtigsten Punkte die Wiedervereinigung der Sch&ouml;pfung der Natur und der Sch&ouml;pfung des Menschen, die seit Jahrhunderten getrennt wurden (z.B. Naturhistorisches und Kunsthistorisches Museum).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Kunst mu&szlig; eine Br&uuml;cke zur Natur schlagen und nicht noch k&uuml;nstlicher werden, d.h. sich noch mehr von der wahren Sch&ouml;pfung entfernen. Wenn der kunstbildende Proze&szlig; bereits gegen die Gesetze der sich selbst schaffenden Natur verst&ouml;&szlig;t, so kann das Resultat kein Kunstwerk im Sinne der Sch&ouml;pfung werden. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Wenn die Bausteine falsch sind, kann kein gutes Haus daraus werden.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Dieser Proze&szlig; des sch&ouml;pferischen Werdens und verantwortungsvollen Entstehens ist sehr langsam und in seinem Beginnstadium scheinbar unscheinbar wie ein ganz junger Baum. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich versuche auch, meine Malerei und mein Leben, meine Werke und Taten konsequent in Einklang zu bringen. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Interessant ist, was Julien Alvard 1954 in Paris zu meiner Ausstellung bei Facchetti schrieb: Il faut beaucoup de s&eacute;rieux pour mener &agrave; bien l&rsquo;ironie d&rsquo;une telle entreprise. Et beaucoup de sens moral pour l&rsquo;appr&eacute;cier. Mais ce s&eacute;rieux lui sera compt&eacute; pour folie, cette folie pour calcul, ce calcul pour pr&eacute;m&eacute;ditation. C&rsquo;est tout &agrave; son honneur...*)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich bin ein gl&uuml;cklicher Mensch, weil alle meine T&auml;tigkeiten auf ein Ziel ausgerichtet sind und sich dort vereinen.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;1. Malerei&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich male hier an vier Bildern: &bdquo;Point de vue chinois&ldquo;, &bdquo;Immigration of an amphibian car&ldquo;, &bdquo;Veena&ldquo; (Cyclone in Tahiti), &bdquo;Das Autokreuz&ldquo; (Weiterentwicklung der Stra&szlig;engekreuzigten). Gleichzeitig an drei japanischen Holzschnitten in enger Zusammenarbeit mit japanischen Meistern in Kioto und Tokio: &bdquo;H&uuml;te tragen Tennos&ldquo; (Tennos fly with hats), &bdquo;Automobil im Regen&ldquo;, &bdquo;Das Ende der Wasser&ldquo;. Die Japaner schneiden Holzbl&ouml;cke nach meinen Anweisungen. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Doch meine gro&szlig;e Bombe lie&szlig; ich vor meiner Abreise in Venedig los: &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es ist mir gelungen, im Siebdruckverfahren eine Auflage von 10.002 St&uuml;ck zu machen, von denen jedes Blatt vom anderen verschieden ist!!! &bdquo;Homo Humus how do you do 860 10002 nights&ldquo;. Die Bl&auml;tter dieser Auflage sind so verschieden wie die Bl&auml;tter eines Baumes. Eine Auflage, die aus Unikaten besteht. &bdquo;A victory of man over chain production using the reproductive machine to produce creative individuality. A big step towards liberation of mankind from the worst enslavement in history: the machine made terror.&rdquo; Ich sende eine Brosch&uuml;re.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;In Neuseeland habe ich einen unglaublichen Sieg errungen. Es ist mir gelungen, von der N.Z. Regierung die Bewilligung zu erlangen, auf meinem Land begraben zu werden. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Dies ist ein erster konkreter Schritt zu einer Revolution im Rahmen des Friedenspaktes mit der Natur und eine erste Anerkennung. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die zuk&uuml;nftigen Friedh&ouml;fe werden &bdquo;Nature reserves&ldquo; sein. Ohne Mauern. Die Toten werden nur so tief bestattet, dass die B&auml;ume, die auf den Gr&auml;bern gepflanzt werden, von den Verstorbenen profitieren. Die Toten sterben nicht, sondern leben in Form von B&auml;umen weiter. Eine tats&auml;chliche Wiedergeburt, eine tats&auml;chliche Wiederauferstehung findet statt.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Friedh&ouml;fe werden zu W&auml;ldern des Lebens. Heute dagegen ist die Bestattung ein Frevel gegen die &Ouml;kologie, gegen das Leben, gegen den Kreislauf, gegen die Wiedergeburt, gegen die kosmischen Gesetze der Natur. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Heute wird ein Keil, eine Betonwand zwischen Tod und Leben gelegt. Eine 4 Meter Gruft, so da&szlig; keine Wurzel hinkann, hermetisch verschlossene S&auml;rge, wo die &Uuml;berreste elendiglich verfaulen, statt Nahrstoff f&uuml;r Leben zu liefern. Die nat&uuml;rliche Vegetation auf dem Grab selbst vergewaltigt mit Zierrasen, Plastikblumen, Betondecke.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Auf meinem &bdquo;Friedhof&ldquo; kann die Natur wachsen, so wie sie will. Auch sterbende B&auml;ume werden nicht beseitigt, sondern nach Gottes Willen belassen, bis die fallenden &Auml;ste und St&auml;mme Humus geworden sind und neuem Leben Basis geben. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;So ein Friedhof ist ein St&uuml;ck Urwald. Ein St&uuml;ck Natur, das wir zur&uuml;ckgeben. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;A piece of territory which man has illegally occupied is given back to nature.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich habe eine Fahne f&uuml;r Neuseeland entworfen. Sende anbei eine Fotokopie des ersten Entwurfes. Habe bereits den Support von mehreren Ministern und von bedeutenden Pers&ouml;nlichkeiten. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Neuseeland sucht sowieso ein neues Symbol. Ich wei&szlig;, das wird einen gro&szlig;en, interessanten Kampf abgeben. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Auch diese Fahne ist im Rahmen des &bdquo;Friedenspaktes mit der Natur&ldquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Meine T&auml;tigkeit als &bdquo;Architekturdoktor&ldquo; erreicht jetzt in Wien einen ersten H&ouml;hepunkt. Am 9. Juli ist Gleichenfeier f&uuml;r das &bdquo;Hundertwasserhaus&ldquo; in der L&ouml;wengasse. Nach 5-j&auml;hrigem Kampf ist es mir gelungen, ein Haus f&uuml;r 50 Familien zu bauen, das total der &bdquo;Bauhausmentalit&auml;t&ldquo; den R&uuml;cken kehrt. Das Fensterrecht der Bewohner ist instituiert zum ersten Mal! Als Vorleistung auf das individuelle Fensterrecht sind alle Fenster verschieden gro&szlig; und an verschiedenen Stellen angebracht. Nicht wie Soldaten genau &uuml;ber und neben einander. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die W&auml;nde sind nicht maschinenglatt, sondern mit der Hand unregelm&auml;&szlig;ig geformt. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Alle D&auml;cher sind bewaldet und mit Wiese versehen. Es wachsen 3 Baummieter aus 3 Fenstern. Durch von mir entworfenen Zwiebelt&uuml;rme und Mosaikeinlagen bekommt das Haus einen romantischen Charakter. Jede Wohnung wird verschieden von der anderen und dies ist auch an der Au&szlig;enmauer erkennbar. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Skyline ist nicht geometrisch gerade. Es gibt einen gro&szlig;en Saal als Wintergarten, eine Fu&szlig;geherzone und vieles mehr. Das Haus ist auch ein Teil des Friedenspaktes mit der Natur: ein &bdquo;natur- und menschengerechtes Haus&ldquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Sende eine Aussendung der Gemeinde Wien.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;5.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Meine T&auml;tigkeit als Vorsteher einer Meisterschule an der Akademie der bildenden K&uuml;nste in Wien stellt sich als ganz gro&szlig;er Erfolg heraus. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Bereits jetzt ist sie die beste Schule an der Akademie. Es kommen ganze Delegationen, Schulklassen, Besucher von &uuml;berall her, um sie zu besuchen. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es gab anfangs Skandale, weil ich eine Schule &uuml;bernehmen mu&szlig;te und unf&auml;hige Sch&uuml;ler hinauswarf, solche, die die Akademie als Obdachlosenasyl f&uuml;r sch&ouml;pferisch Unf&auml;hige betrachteten und nur wegen Studienbeitr&auml;gen dort herumlungerten.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Auch weil ich die Schule in einen Wald verwandelte.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Man stelle sich vor: Der Vorsteher der &bdquo;Meisterklasse Hundertwasser&ldquo; ist fast st&auml;ndig abwesend und &uuml;bergibt die Lehrt&auml;tigkeit den B&auml;umen und Pflanzen, die er aus dem Palmenhaus in der Schule aufstellen lie&szlig;.&lt;u&gt; Meine Abwesenheit erzeugt meine Anwesenheit!&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Und die Rechnung, so absurd sie klingt, geht auf. Sieben hervorragende Meister haben sich durch sich selbst in dieser sch&ouml;pfungsgetr&auml;nkten Atmosph&auml;re gebildet, wo auch die sauerstoffangereicherte Luft um ein Vielfaches besser ist als in den anderen Malschulen:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Karin K&ouml;ppl&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; M&auml;rchenwelt&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Markus Schiller&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ein junger Phantast&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Christian Rausch&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ein neuer Schiele, jedoch ganz anders&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Bruno Richard&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ein echter Naiver, ein Franzose&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Anna Stangl&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; beseelte Landschaften&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Martina Hanadou&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; erz&auml;hlende Malerei, wie eine Hieroglyphenschrift&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Maria Trummer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; eine ganz junge Realistin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Keiner&lt;/u&gt; und &lt;u&gt;keine&lt;/u&gt; davon imitiert Hundertwasser oder irgend jemanden anderen! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Ein unglaublicher Sieg durch eine g&auml;nzlich neuartige Lehrmethode.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Schicke sp&auml;ter Reproduktionen in einem Kalender vereinigt!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Au&szlig;er den riesigen B&auml;umen stehen noch 2 Pflanzenwasserkl&auml;ranlagen in meiner Schule. Es sind Wasserpflanzen, die in Kaskaden &uuml;bereinander Schmutzwasser reinigen und beim Hindurchlaufen pl&auml;tschert das Wasser wie ein leiser Bach. Es entsteht eine halbe Stunde &bdquo;Bachmusik&ldquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Ferner habe ich innerhalb meiner Lehrt&auml;tigkeit einen Lehrauftrag etabliert, namens: &bdquo;Natur -Kunst - Sch&ouml;pfung&ldquo;, wo bedeutende Wissenschaftler, Nobelpreistr&auml;ger zum Thema der Wiedervereinigung Natur - Kunst Stellung nehmen.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Lieber Freund Aberbach,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Sie sehen, warum ich eigentlich zufrieden und stolz mit mir selbst sein kann. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Es freut mich immer, wenn das, was man mir als &bdquo;Publicity-T&auml;tigkeit&ldquo; auslegt, sich im sp&auml;teren als sehr, sehr ernste, ja zukunftsnotwendige Pioniertaten erweisen und es mir gelingt, immer neue Taten zu setzen, die unweigerlich zuerst immer als unlautere, ja sogar profitorientierte Machenschaften gebrandmarkt werden.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Lieber Freund Aberbach,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;ich freue mich Ihnen, eigentlich als einzigen Menschen, diesen &Uuml;berblick &uuml;ber meine letzten T&auml;tigkeiten ausf&uuml;hrlich zu berichten. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Es freut mich, dass wir Freunde geblieben sind &uuml;ber so viele Jahre hinweg. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Bitte nicht vergessen, mir eine genaue Liste der Bilder zu schicken, die aus der Sammlung Aberbach in andere Sammlungen &uuml;bergingen, mit genauen Angaben der neuen Besitzer und der Adressen. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Sie wissen, wie sehr ich seelisch mit meinen Werken verbunden bin, die ich als meine Kinder betrachte. Auch war dies eine Bedingung, als ich die Bilder hergab. Bitte, im Interesse unserer langen und zuk&uuml;nftigen Freundschaft!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Sind Bilder von mir beim Brand im Haus Ihres Bruders in Paris besch&auml;digt oder vernichtet worden?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Es ist Abend geworden im Kaurinui-Tal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Die neuen Fahnen wehen von 3 Fahnenstangen.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Herzlich Ihr&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Mit Gru&szlig; an Ihre Frau und Ihre Kinder.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;*) Es braucht viel an Ernsthaftigkeit, um die Ironie aus so einem Unterfangen herauszuhalten, &nbsp;und viel Sinn f&uuml;r Moral um es zu w&uuml;rdigen. Aber diese Ernsthaftigkeit wird ihm als Verr&uuml;cktheit angekreidet, diese Verr&uuml;cktheit f&uuml;r Berechnung, die Berechnung f&uuml;r Vors&auml;tzlichkeit. Es gereicht ihm alles zur Ehre&hellip;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_occasion_en-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;Written in Kaurinui&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;Valley on 23 June 1984.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;',
text_occasion_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Geschrieben in Kaurinui Valley am 23. Juni 1984.&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. (Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag: Munich, 2004, pp. 66-70 (German)&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag: M&uuml;nchen, 2004, S. 66-70&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_author-'Hundertwasser',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'',
text_source_ge-'',
text_excerpt-'',
text_origin-''
]).

