text_keywords-'ecologist, peace treaty, civilization, straight line, rationalism, creativity, illiteracy, &Ouml;kologe, Friedensvertrag, Zivilisation, gerade Linie, Rationalismus, Kreativit&auml;t, Analphabetismus',
