text_keywords-'decorative, geometric, organic, biological, vegetative, straight line, atheism, crystal, nature, dekorativ, geometrisch, organisch, biologisch, vegetativ, gerade Linie, Atheismus, Kristall, Natur',
text_date-'1978-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;The spiral existed long before Hundertwasser. But it had no importance in the history of art at the precise moment in which he gained his reputation as a painter. It was considered then as a mythological, decorative, or geometric element.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;His spiral is organic, biological, and vegetative. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;This organic spiral denounces the atheism of the straight line and its fundamental non-creativity. The straight line is about to&nbsp; be unmasked by the vegetative spiral. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;The latest victory of the spiral over the straight line is the law of growth of crystals. Microscopic examinations have revealed that crystals are formed by successive spiraloid stratifications, like winding staircases. The spiral growth of crystals is the living proof that the straight line does not exist in nature.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;The spiral existed long before Hundertwasser. But it had no importance in the history of art at the precise moment in which he gained his reputation as a painter. It was considered then as a mythological, decorative, or geometric element.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;His spiral is organic, biological, and vegetative. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;This organic spiral denounces the atheism of the straight line and its fundamental non-creativity. The straight line is about to&nbsp; be unmasked by the vegetative spiral. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;The latest victory of the spiral over the straight line is the law of growth of crystals. Microscopic examinations have revealed that crystals are formed by successive spiraloid stratifications, like winding staircases. The spiral growth of crystals is the living proof that the straight line does not exist in nature.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Die Spirale existierte lange vor Hundertwasser. Aber sie hatte keine Bedeutung in der Kunst in dem Moment, in dem er seine Anerkennung als Maler fand. Damals wurde sie f&uuml;r ein mythologisches, dekoratives oder geometrisches Element gehalten.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Seine Spirale ist organisch, biologisch und vegetativ. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Diese organische Spirale bringt die Gottlosigkeit der geraden Linie zu Tage und ihre fundamentale Unkreativit&auml;t. Die gerade Linie wird durch die vegetative Spirale entlarvt. (...)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Der neueste Sieg der Spirale &uuml;ber die gerade Linie ist das Gesetz vom Wachstum der Kristalle.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Mikroskopische Untersuchungen haben enth&uuml;llt, da&szlig; Kristalle durch sukzessive spiralf&ouml;rmige Schichtung geformt werden, &auml;hnlich sich windender Stiegenl&auml;ufe. Das spiralf&ouml;rmige Wachstum von Kristallen ist der lebende Beweis daf&uuml;r, da&szlig; die gerade Linie in der Natur nicht existiert.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Pierre Restany',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Restany, Pierre: Happy Hundertwasser - Hundertwasser Heureux. Ballantine Books: New York, 1978, pp. 25-27&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_source_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Restany Pierre: Happy Hundertwasser - Hundertwasser Heureux. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Ballantine Books: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;New   York&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt; 1978, S. 25f.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
