%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.1.6.5.1
object(text,'1.1.6.5.1','On Hundertwasser\'s Text \"Real Freedom\"',[
id-97,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-97,
txt-'1.1.6.5.1',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'On Hundertwasser&#039;s Text &quot;Real Freedom&quot;',
text_title_ge-'Zu Hundertwassers Text &quot;Die wahre Freiheit&quot;',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'2004-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;This polemically engaged piece of writing evokes scepticism regarding the assessment of timely progress. In it he formulated for the first time what became a program in his later manifesto, entitled &lt;em&gt;Die Kehrtwendung &lt;/em&gt;[The Turn].&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser demands a step back in the face of development which has arrived at the abyss. One-dimensionality of thought and action has to give way to a diversity which digs its own grave. The individual must learn to distrust, to refuse and to abdicate that which the institutions of modernism present as progress and achievement.&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;This polemically engaged piece of writing evokes scepticism regarding the assessment of timely progress. In it he formulated for the first time what became a program in his later manifesto, entitled &lt;em&gt;Die Kehrtwendung &lt;/em&gt;[The Turn].&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser demands a step back in the face of development which has arrived at the abyss. One-dimensionality of thought and action has to give way to a diversity in order not to digs its own grave. The individual must learn to distrust, to refuse and to abdicate that which the institutions of modernism present as progress and achievement.&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Diese polemisch engagierte Schrift meldet Zweifel an, wenn es um die Bewertung des zeitgerechten Fortschritts geht. In ihr ist zum ersten Mal formuliert, was in seinem sp&auml;teren Manifest &raquo;Die Kehrtwendung&laquo; zum Programm erhoben ist.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser fordert den R&uuml;ckschritt angesichts einer Entwicklung, die sich vor dem Abgrund befindet. Die Eindimensionalit&auml;t des Denkens und Handelns mu&szlig; dabei einer Vielf&auml;ltigkeit weichen, will sie sich nicht ihr eigenes Grab schaufeln. Der Einzelne mu&szlig; lernen, zu mi&szlig;trauen, sich zu verweigern und dem zu entsagen, was die Institutionen der modernen Zeiten an Fortschritten und Errungenschaften vorlegen.&lt;/p&gt;',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Walter Schurian',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-ansi-language: DE; mso-fareast-language: DE; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-ansi-language: EN-GB; mso-fareast-language: DE; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA&quot;&gt;(Beautiful Paths, Thoughts on Art and Life), Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag: Munich, 2004, p. 309&lt;/span&gt;',
text_source_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt&quot;&gt;Walter Schurian (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben, &lt;/span&gt;M&uuml;nchen: Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, 2004, S. 309&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_excerpt-'',
text_origin-''
]).

%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.1.6.6
object(text,'1.1.6.6','FROM A CREATIVE KNOWLEDGE TO CREATIVE IGNORANCE',[
id-100,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-100,
txt-'1.1.6.6',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'FROM A CREATIVE KNOWLEDGE TO CREATIVE IGNORANCE',
text_title_ge-'VOM SCH&Ouml;PFERISCH WISSENDEN ZUM UNWISSENDEN',
text_keywords-'illiteracy, knowledge, child, ignorant, education, creative impotence, childhood,
Analphabetentum, Wissen, Kind, Ignorant, Erziehung, sch&ouml;pferische Impotenz, Kindheit',
text_date-'1981-08-07',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Our real illiteracy is not the ignorance to read and write and not the incapability to repeat other people&rsquo;s knowledge, but the inability to create.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;A child possesses this creative ability, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;the seemingly illiterate, seemingly ignorant child &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;is not ignorant and not illiterate at all. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;On the contrary, it is in full possession of his own creative powers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;By our educational system, he is being degraded to a true creative illiterate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;For the grown-up, who suffers &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;under this creative impotence, which was forced onto him, the only possibility left is to return to his own childhood and to st&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;art &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;again from the last moment, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;where he was dragged out of his dreams. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;But these dreams were not just longings, but his real basis, without which he can never grow into a human being.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Our real illiteracy is not the ignorance to read and write and not the incapability to repeat other people&rsquo;s knowledge, but the inability to create.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;A child possesses this creative ability, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;the seemingly illiterate, seemingly ignorant child &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;is not ignorant and not illiterate at all. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;On the contrary, it is in full possession of his own creative powers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;By our educational system, he is being degraded to a true creative illiterate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;For the grown-up, who suffers &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;under this creative impotence, which was forced onto him, the only possibility left is to return to his own childhood and to st&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;art &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;again from the last moment, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;where he was dragged out of his dreams. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;But these dreams were not just longings, but his real basis, without which he can never grow into a human being.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;unser wahres analphabetentum ist nicht &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;das unverm&ouml;gen, lesen und schreiben zu k&ouml;nnen, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;sondern das unverm&ouml;gen, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;wahrhaft sch&ouml;pFerisch t&auml;tig zu sein.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;das kind besitzt diese sch&ouml;pferische f&auml;higkeit. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;das scheinbar analphabetische, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;scheinbar unwissende kind ist gar nicht unwissend &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;und gar kein analphabet, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;sondern ein sch&ouml;pferisch wissender, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;und wird erst durch unser erziehungssystem &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;zum wahren analphabeten, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;zum sch&ouml;pferisch unwissenden degradiert.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;dem erwachsenen, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;der unter der sch&ouml;pferischen impotenz leidet, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;die ihm anerzogen wurde, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;bleibt nur die m&ouml;glichkeit, sich an seine eigene kindheit zur&uuml;ckzuerinnern und dort anzukn&uuml;Pfen,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;dort foRtzusetzen, wo man ihn aus seinen tr&auml;umen r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;ISS&lt;span style=&quot;text-transform: uppercase&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;die gar keine tr&auml;ume waren, sondern seine reale basis, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; text-transform: uppercase; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;die wurzel seiner existenz, ohne die er nie und nimmer wahrhaftig Mensch sein kann.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_occasion_en-'Written in Salzburg on 7 August 1981 as a &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;forword for a brochure on the occasion of the international travelling exhibition of the &lt;em&gt;SOS-Kinderd&ouml;rfer&lt;/em&gt; &raquo;Kinder Kunst&laquo; (Art by children), Palais Palffy, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;, September/October, 1981 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;(German)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;',
text_occasion_ge-'Geschrieben am 7. August 1981 als &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Vorwort f&uuml;r eine Brosch&uuml;re anl&auml;&szlig;lich der internationalen Wander-Ausstellung der SOS-Kinderd&ouml;rfer &raquo;Kinder Kunst&laquo;, Palais Palffy, Wien, September/Oktober 1981. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;',
text_published_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Brochure:&nbsp;&raquo;Kinder Kunst&laquo; (Art by children),&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Vienna,&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;1981 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;(German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. (Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): Munich, 1983, pp. 82-83 and ed. 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, Munich), p. 99 (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schmied, Wieland (ed.): Hundertwasser 1928&ndash;2000, Catalogue Raisonn&eacute;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Vol. II: F&uuml;rst, Andrea Christa: Catalogue Raisonn&eacute;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Taschen: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Cologne&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;, 2002, pp. 912-913 (German and English)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Brosch&uuml;re: &raquo;Kinder Kunst&laquo;, Wien 1981&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): M&uuml;nchen 1983, S. 82-83 und Ausgabe 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, M&uuml;nchen), S. 99&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schmied, Wieland (Hg.): Hundertwasser 1928&ndash;2000, Catalogue Raisonn&eacute; / Werkverzeichnis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Vol. II: F&uuml;rst, Andrea Christa: Catalogue Raisonn&eacute; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;/ Werkverzeichnis. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Taschen: K&ouml;ln 2002, S. 912-913 (Deutsch und Englisch)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_author-'Hundertwasser',
text_orig_lang-'',
