%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.3.2.2.1
object(text,'1.3.2.2.1','Los von Loose MORE',[
id-106,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-106,
txt-'1.3.2.2.1',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'Los von Loose MORE',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1998-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s hatred of rationalism, coupled with a maniacal individualism, placed Hundertwasser the prophet in a position more and more overtly critical of society. It was again in the nude that in Vienna in 1968 he protested against barren rectilinear architecture [Nude demonstration against rationalism in architecture at the International Student Hostel, Vienna, January 25, 1968], by way of a prelude to the reading of his &ldquo;Los von Loos&rdquo; manifesto boycotting architecture [February 9, 1968 at the Concordia Hall in Vienna]. The opportunity for that virulent action was given him by the sixtieth anniversary of the publication in 1908 of the architect Adolf Loos&rsquo; famous book &ldquo;Ornament and Crime&rdquo;. [&hellip;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s hatred of rationalism, coupled with a maniacal individualism, placed Hundertwasser the prophet in a position more and more overtly critical of society. It was again in the nude that in Vienna in 1968 he protested against barren rectilinear architecture [Nude demonstration against rationalism in architecture at the International Student Hostel, Vienna, January 25, 1968], by way of a prelude to the reading of his &ldquo;Los von Loos&rdquo; manifesto boycotting architecture [February 9, 1968 at the Concordia Hall in Vienna]. The opportunity for that virulent action was given him by the sixtieth anniversary of the publication in 1908 of the architect Adolf Loos&rsquo; famous book &ldquo;Ornament and Crime&rdquo;. [&hellip;] &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Der Ha&szlig; auf den Rationalismus, zusammen mit einem unb&auml;ndigen Individualismus, bringt den Propheten Hundertwasser zunehmend in eine Position der offenen Kritik an der Gesellschaft. Abermals nackt protestiert Hundertwasser 1968 in Wien gegen die sterile rechtwinklige Architektur [Nackdemonstration im Internationalen Studentenheim, 25. 1. 1968, Anm.], als Pr&auml;ambel zur Verlesung seines Manifestes &bdquo;Los von Loos&ldquo; und des Aufrufs zum Boykott der Architektur [am 9. Februar 1968 im Concordiasaal in Wien, Anm.]. Der Anla&szlig; f&uuml;r diese provokante Aktion war der 60. Jahrestag der Ver&ouml;ffentlichung des ber&uuml;hmten Buches des Architekten Adolf Loos im Jahr 1908: &bdquo;Ornament und Verbrechen&ldquo;. &lt;/p&gt;',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Pierre Restany',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Restany, Pierre: The Power of Art. Hundertwasser &ndash; The Painter-King with the five Skins. Taschen: Cologne, 1998, p. 26&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;',
text_source_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Restany, Pierre: Die Macht der Kunst. Hundertwasser &ndash; Der Maler-K&ouml;nig mit den f&uuml;nf H&auml;uten. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 1998, S. 26&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_excerpt-'',
text_origin-''
]).

%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.3.2.3
object(text,'1.3.2.3','CALL TO ALL RESIDENTS',[
id-108,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-108,
txt-'1.3.2.3',
text_type-10,
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'CALL TO ALL RESIDENTS',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1968-03-07',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time has come.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of surveillance is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of waiting to paradise is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of fruitless talking is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of action has come.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;I give houses back to people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Not merely pro forma, but in reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;As from now it is the right and duty of all residents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;of smooth, prison-like boxes to reshape them with&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;their own hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Outside and inside, wherever they live.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Without instruction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;They begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;by painting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;the white entrance door leading onto the corridor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;and the white uniform window frames&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;in red or green or whatever they like.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;In particular outside,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;so they can recognise their windows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;when they come home tired.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Woe to the authorities,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;woe to laws or anything&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;forbidding such an obvious and natural right.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Woe to the architects!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;It is the duty of every architect to demand and procure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;the total individual right to building alterations for the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;residents of the houses he is building or has already built!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Otherwise his conscience will give him no peace!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time has come.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of surveillance is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of waiting to paradise is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of fruitless talking is past.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;The time of action has come.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;I give houses back to people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Not merely pro forma, but in reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;As from now it is the right and duty of all residents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;of smooth, prison-like boxes to reshape them with&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;their own hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Outside and inside, wherever they live.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Without instruction.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;They begin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;by painting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;the white entrance door leading onto the corridor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;and the white uniform window frames&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;in red or green or whatever they like.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;In particular outside,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;so they can recognise their windows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;when they come home tired.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Woe to the authorities,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;woe to laws or anything&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;forbidding such an obvious and natural right.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Woe to the architects!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;It is the duty of every architect to demand and procure&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;the total individual right to building alterations for the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;residents of the houses he is building or has already built!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Otherwise his conscience will give him no peace!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Zeit ist gekommen. Die Zeit der Beaufsichtigung ist vorbei. Die Zeit des Wartens auf das Paradies ist vorbei. Die Zeit des unfruchtbaren Redens ist vorbei. Die Zeit des Tuns ist da &middot; Ich gebe die H&auml;user den Menschen zur&uuml;ck. Nicht nur zum Schein, sondern wirklich.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es ist ab jetzt Recht und Pflicht jedes Bewohners von Gef&auml;ngnissen gleicher glatter Schachteln, diese eigenh&auml;ndig umzuformen. Au&szlig;en und innen, genau dort, wo er wohnt. Ohne Bevormundung &middot; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;Er beginnt damit, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;seine &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;wei&szlig;e Einheits-T&uuml;r zum Gang, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;seine &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;wei&szlig;en Einheits-Fensterrahmen zu streichen in Rot oder in Gr&uuml;n oder wie er es liebt. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;Besonders au&szlig;en, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;damit er &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;sein &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;Fenster erkennen kann, wenn er m&uuml;de nach Hause kommt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Wehe &lt;/em&gt;wenn eine Beh&ouml;rde, &lt;em&gt;wehe &lt;/em&gt;wenn ein Gesetz oder irgendwas ihm das verbieten, was selbstverst&auml;ndlich ist &middot; &lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;Wehe &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;den Architekten! Es ist die &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;Pflicht &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;jedes Architekten, das &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;totale individuelle Bauver&auml;nderungs-Recht &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;f&uuml;r die Bewohner des Hauses, das er gerade baut oder gebaut hat, zu fordern und zu erwirken &lt;/span&gt;&middot; &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.4pt&quot;&gt;Sonst wird ihm das Gewissen keine Ruhe lassen!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Written in Venice on 7 March 1968.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;The text is an annex to the manifesto &raquo;Los von Loos&laquo; (Loose from Loos).&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;',
text_occasion_ge-'Geschrieben am 7. M&auml;rz 1968 in Venedig.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Der Text ist ein Annex zum Manifest &raquo;Los von Loos&laquo;.&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_published_en-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s private print with manifestos and speeches in the nude in 1967 and 1968. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma; letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Vienna, 2&lt;sup&gt;nd&lt;/sup&gt; edition, 1968 (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. (Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): Munich, 1983, p. 157 and ed. 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, Munich), p. 210 (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Das Hundertwasser Haus (The Hundertwasser House). &Ouml;sterreichischer Bundesverlag/Compress Verlag: Vienna, 1985, p. 100 (&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;German&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Rand, Harry: Friedensreich Hundertwasser. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Taschen: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Cologne&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;, 1991, p. 168, abridged edition 1993 and edition 2003, p. 146 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Niggemeier, Friedhelm: Kunstwerke. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;(Works of Art) Begleitheft f&uuml;r die Schulgalerie. Sekundarstufe II. Ernst Klett Verlag: Stuttgart, 1996, p. 61 (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black; font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser Architecture. For a More Human Architecture in Harmony with Nature. Taschen: Cologne, 1997, p. 76 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black; font-family: Tahoma&quot;&gt;(English) and German edition 2006, p. 58 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Hundertwassers Privatdruck &uuml;ber die Manifeste und die Nacktreden 1967 und 1968. &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;Wien, 2. Auflage&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;1968&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): M&uuml;nchen 1983, S. 157 und Ausgabe 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, M&uuml;nchen), S. 210 &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Das Hundertwasser Haus. &Ouml;sterreichischer Bundesverlag/Compress Verlag: Wien 1985, S. 100&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Rand, Harry: Friedensreich Hundertwasser. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 1991, S. 168, gek&uuml;rzte Ausgabe 1993 und Ausgabe 2003, S. 146&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Niggemeier, Friedhelm: Kunstwerke. Begleitheft f&uuml;r die Schulgalerie. Sekundarstufe II. Ernst Klett Verlag: Stuttgart, 1996, S. 61&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser Architektur. F&uuml;r ein natur- und menschengerechteres Bauen. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 1996, S. 76 und erweiterte Neuausgabe 2006, S. 58&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
