%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.3.3.4.1.1
object(text,'1.3.3.4.1.1','Tree-tenant initiative, Milan MORE',[
id-121,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-121,
txt-'1.3.3.4.1.1',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'Tree-tenant initiative, Milan MORE',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1997-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;font size=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=\&quot;Times New Roman\&quot;&gt;A year later [1973], this time in Milan, Hundertwasser again tried to put this thesis across. Having been invited by Giulio Macchi to participate in &ldquo;Arte Citt&agrave;&rdquo; (city art) as part of the Milan Triennial, Hundertwasser submitted his &ldquo;inquilino albero&rdquo; (tree tenant). Hundertwasser had 15 trees, roots and all, lifted up to fifteen flats on Via Manzoni and planted them so that they stuck out into the street. Without heeding the risk of breaching the borders of the decorative and despite the indifference of most of the passers-by, Hundertwasser had achieved his aim of demonstrating the thesis of window right and tree obligation in the centre of a metropolis.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;font size=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=\&quot;Times New Roman\&quot;&gt;A year later [1973], this time in Milan, Hundertwasser again tried to put this thesis across. Having been invited by Giulio Macchi to participate in &ldquo;Arte Citt&agrave;&rdquo; (city art) as part of the Milan Triennial, Hundertwasser submitted his &ldquo;inquilino albero&rdquo; (tree tenant). Hundertwasser had 15 trees, roots and all, lifted up to fifteen flats on Via Manzoni and planted them so that they stuck out into the street. Without heeding the risk of breaching the borders of the decorative and despite the indifference of most of the passers-by, Hundertwasser had achieved his aim of demonstrating the thesis of window right and tree obligation in the centre of a metropolis.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'Ein Jahr sp&auml;ter [1973, Anm.], diesmal in Mailand, versuchte Hundertwasser sich von neuem mit seiner These. Von Giulio Macchi eingeladen, an der &bdquo;Arte Citt&agrave;&ldquo; (Stadtkunst) im Rahmen der Mail&auml;nder Triennale teilzunehmen, lieferte Hundertwasser den Beitrag &bdquo;Inquilino albero&ldquo; (Baummieter). Hundertwasser lie&szlig; 15 B&auml;ume mit Wurzeln und allem Drum und Dran zu verschiedenenen Appartements in der Via Manzoni hieven und pflanzte sie dann in 15 Wohnungen so, da&szlig; sie auf die Stra&szlig;e herausragten. Ungeachtet des Risikos, an die Grenzen des Dekorativen zu sto&szlig;en, und trotz der Gleichg&uuml;ltigkeit der meisten Passanten hatte Hundertwasser sein Ziel erreicht, im Herzen einer Gro&szlig;stadt die These des Fensterrechts und der Baumpflicht zu demonstrieren.',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Pierre Restany',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'&lt;font size=\&quot;3\&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=\&quot;Times New Roman\&quot;&gt;Pierre Restany, in: Hundertwasser Architectur, For a more human architecture in harmony with nature, Cologne: Benedikt Taschen Verlag, 1997, p. 88&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_source_ge-'',
text_excerpt-'',
text_origin-''
]).

%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.3.3.4.2
object(text,'1.3.3.4.2','TO THE OCCUPANTS OF A BUILDING ON ALSERBACHSTRASSE IN VIENNA',[
id-122,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-122,
txt-'1.3.3.4.2',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'TO THE OCCUPANTS OF A BUILDING ON ALSERBACHSTRASSE IN VIENNA',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1980-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Dear Resident,&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;We are pleased to be able to contribute to the improvement of the quality of life in your area. In you building five tree tenants will move in according to plans designed by Hundertwasser. The tree tenants will occupy a loggia-like living area of about four square metres which will be detached from human living space.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;There will be three tree tenants on the first storey directly above the bank and two tree tenants growing directly out of the bank on the ground floor. The advantages of having tree tenants in one&rsquo;s own house are undisputed and manifold.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;As the street is largely ruled out for planting trees due to the traffic and subterranean conduits, roof greenery mostly takes on a penthouse nature and remains invisible to the man on the street and is often unfeasible for constructional reasons, the vertical building facades are an alternative for establishing a forest in the city.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Here are just some of the advantages:&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants, trees growing out of the windows, are visible from afar and benefit many people.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants produce oxygen.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants improve the urban and residential climate considerably by mitigating the humid &ndash; dry and warm &ndash; cold contrasts. Fewer headaches &ndash; more well-being.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants are a perfect dust-absorbing and dust-filtering system. In particular, the fine, toxic dust which even vacuum cleaners cannot suck up is largely neutralised and removed in the area of tree tenants. The housewife will have less dust in her apartment.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Street noise is significantly reduced, as the echo effect of the vertical canyons of buildings is muffled.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants form a partial screen and produce a sense of security.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Since the tree tenants must make do with a few cubic metres of earth, they cannot develop into big trees. Their capacity for furnishing shade will thus remain very limited. So sun and light easily reach the windows the tree tenants are growing out of, too, particularly in the winter, when the leaves have fallen.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;No trouble from spiders and ants, as they do not live in trees. But hopefully butterflies and birds will come.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;In this way beauty and a living source of joy will be restored in a co-existence with a piece of nature in one&rsquo;s own house.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Dear Resident,&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;We are pleased to be able to contribute to the improvement of the quality of life in your area. In you building five tree tenants will move in according to plans designed by Hundertwasser. The tree tenants will occupy a loggia-like living area of about four square metres which will be detached from human living space.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;There will be three tree tenants on the first storey directly above the bank and two tree tenants growing directly out of the bank on the ground floor. The advantages of having tree tenants in one&rsquo;s own house are undisputed and manifold.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;As the street is largely ruled out for planting trees due to the traffic and subterranean conduits, roof greenery mostly takes on a penthouse nature and remains invisible to the man on the street and is often unfeasible for constructional reasons, the vertical building facades are an alternative for establishing a forest in the city.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Here are just some of the advantages:&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants, trees growing out of the windows, are visible from afar and benefit many people.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants produce oxygen.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants improve the urban and residential climate considerably by mitigating the humid &ndash; dry and warm &ndash; cold contrasts. Fewer headaches &ndash; more well-being.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants are a perfect dust-absorbing and dust-filtering system. In particular, the fine, toxic dust which even vacuum cleaners cannot suck up is largely neutralised and removed in the area of tree tenants. The housewife will have less dust in her apartment.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Street noise is significantly reduced, as the echo effect of the vertical canyons of buildings is muffled.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Tree tenants form a partial screen and produce a sense of security.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Since the tree tenants must make do with a few cubic metres of earth, they cannot develop into big trees. Their capacity for furnishing shade will thus remain very limited. So sun and light easily reach the windows the tree tenants are growing out of, too, particularly in the winter, when the leaves have fallen.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;No trouble from spiders and ants, as they do not live in trees. But hopefully butterflies and birds will come.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;In this way beauty and a living source of joy will be restored in a co-existence with a piece of nature in one&rsquo;s own house.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Liebe Hausbewohner!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Wir freuen uns, einen Beitrag zur Verbesserung der Lebensqualit&auml;t in Ihrem Bereich leisten zu k&ouml;nnen. In Ihrem Haus werden f&uuml;nf Baummieter nach Entw&uuml;rfen von Hundertwasser einziehen. Die Baummieter bewohnen einen zirka vier Quadratmeter gro&szlig;en loggiaartigen Wohnbereich, welcher vom menschlichen Wohnraum fachgerecht getrennt wird.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Es werden drei Baummieter aus Fenstern im ersten Stock direkt &uuml;ber der Zentralsparkasse und zwei Baummieter zu ebener Erde direkt aus der Bank herauswachsen. Die Vorteile hauseigener Baummieter sind unbestritten und vielf&auml;ltig.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Da die Stra&szlig;e wegen des Verkehrs und den Untergrundeinrichtungen f&uuml;r Baumpflanzungen weitgehend ausf&auml;llt, Dachbepflanzungen jedoch meist Penthousecharakter annehmen und f&uuml;r den Mann der Stra&szlig;e unsichtbar beleiben und auch aus konstruktionellen Gr&uuml;nden oft unm&ouml;glich sind, bieten sich die senkrechten Hausfassaden zu einer Bewaldung der Stadt an.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hier nur einige der Vorteile: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;1. Baummieter, das hei&szlig;t B&auml;ume, die aus dem Fenster wachsen, sind weithin sichtbar und kommen vielen Menschen zugute.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;2.&nbsp; Baummieter erzeugen Sauerstoff.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;3.&nbsp; Baummieter verbessern das Stadt- und Wohnklima betr&auml;chtlich durch Milderung der Feucht-Trocken-Warm-Kalt-Gegens&auml;tze. Weniger Kopfweh - mehr Wohlbefinden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;4.&nbsp; Baummieter sind eine perfekte Staubschluck- und Staub&shy;filter&shy;anlage. Beson&shy;ders der feine, giftige Staub, den auch die Staubsauger nicht schlu&shy;cken k&ouml;nnen, wird von den Baummietern in ihrem Be&shy;reich weitge&shy;hend neu&shy;tralisiert und abgebaut. Die Hausfrau hat weni&shy;ger Staub in den Woh&shy;nungen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;5.&nbsp; Der Stra&szlig;enl&auml;rm wird bedeutend gemildert, da die Echowirkung der senk&shy;rechten H&auml;userschluchten einged&auml;mmt wird.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;6.&nbsp; Baummieter bilden einen teilweisen Sichtschutz und erzeugen Ge&shy;borgenheit.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;7.&nbsp; Da die Baummieter mit wenigen Kubikmetern Erde auskommen m&uuml;ssen, k&ouml;nnen sie sich nicht zu gro&szlig;en B&auml;umen entwickeln. Daher wird die schattenspendende Eigenschaft sehr beschr&auml;nkt blieben. Sonne und Licht gelangen also gut auch an die Fenster, vor denen Baummieter wachsen, insbesondere im Winter, wenn die Bl&auml;tter abge&shy;fallen sind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;8. Keine Bel&auml;stigung durch Spinnen und Ameisen, da diese nicht in B&auml;umen wohnen. Hoffentlich kommen jedoch Schmetterlinge und V&ouml;gel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;9.&nbsp; So kommt die Sch&ouml;nheit und Lebensfreude wieder im Zusam&shy;menleben mit einem St&uuml;ck haus&shy;eigener Na&shy;tur.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;Written for Tree-tenant initiative, Alserbachstrasse, 1980/81.&lt;/span&gt;',
text_occasion_ge-'&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Roman proportional&quot;; letter-spacing: 0.2pt&quot;&gt;Baummieter Aktion, Alserbachstra&szlig;e, 1980/81&lt;/span&gt;',
text_published_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. (Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): Munich, 1983, pp. 158-159 and ed. 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, Munich), pp. 210-211 (German)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Das Hundertwasser Haus (The Hundertwasser House). &Ouml;sterreichischer Bundesverlag/Compress Verlag: Vienna, 1985, pp. 116-117 (German)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser Architecture. For a More Human Architecture in Harmony with Nature. Taschen: Cologne, 1997, pp. 82-84 (English) and German edition 2006, pp. 64-66 &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Eichheim, Hubert; Bovermann, Monika; Tesa&#345;ov&aacute;, Lea et al.: Blaue Blume. Deutsch als Fremdsprache. Kursbuch &ndash; Englische Ausgabe. Max Hueber Verlag: Ismaning/Germany, 2002, p. 329 (German)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_published_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Deutscher Taschenbuch Verlag (dtv): M&uuml;nchen 1983, S. 158-159 und Ausgabe 2004 (Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag, M&uuml;nchen), S. 210-211&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;letter-spacing: 0.3pt&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Das Hundertwasser Haus. &Ouml;sterreichischer Bundesverlag/Compress Verlag: Wien 1985, S. 116-117&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser Architektur. F&uuml;r ein natur- und menschengerechteres Bauen. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 1996, S. 82-84 und erweiterte Neuausgabe 2006, S. 64-66&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;Eichheim, Hubert; Bovermann, Monika; Tesa&#345;ov&aacute;, Lea et al.: Blaue Blume. Deutsch als Fremdsprache. Kursbuch &ndash; Englische Ausgabe. Max Hueber Verlag: Ismaning/Deutschland, 2002, S. 329 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;margin-left: 14.2pt; text-indent: -14.2pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
