text_origin-''
]).

%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.4.1.3
object(text,'1.4.1.3','Hundertwasser Postage Stamps - A Chronology MORE',[
id-226,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-226,
txt-'1.4.1.3',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'Hundertwasser Postage Stamps - A Chronology MORE',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'2006-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser collected postage stamps as a child, and they were for him a window on to the world and a signpost towards painting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;His enthusiasm for stamps remained with him his whole life long. He put great importance to the fact that when he had to send a letter or a card, he would always use particularly beautiful stamps. For important post he stuck on several stamps so the appearance of the envelope would be particularly colourful and varied. For him stamps were ambassadors of a country and its culture, its landscape and uniqueness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser was invited to design stamps for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Senegal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;, the United Nations, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Liechtenstein&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Luxembourg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt; and many other countries. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s stamps have for years been desirable and much sought-after objects for collectors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_contents_en-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser collected postage stamps as a child, and they were for him a window on to the world and a signpost towards painting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;His enthusiasm for stamps remained with him his whole life long. He put great importance to the fact that when he had to send a letter or a card, he would always use particularly beautiful stamps. For important post he stuck on several stamps so the appearance of the envelope would be particularly colourful and varied. For him stamps were ambassadors of a country and its culture, its landscape and uniqueness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser was invited to design stamps for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Senegal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;, the United Nations, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Liechtenstein&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Luxembourg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt; and many other countries. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser&rsquo;s stamps have for years been desirable and much sought-after objects for collectors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black&quot;&gt;Schon als Kind hat Hundertwasser Briefmarken gesammelt, sie waren ihm Fenster zur Welt und Wegweiser zur Malerei. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black&quot;&gt;Die Begeisterung f&uuml;r Briefmarken hat ihn sein Leben lang begleitet. Er hat gro&szlig;en Wert darauf gelegt, wann immer er einen Brief oder eine Karte verschickte, besonders sch&ouml;ne Marken zu verwenden. Er hat f&uuml;r das notwendige Porto immer mehrere Marken aufgeklebt, damit das Erscheinungsbild des Kuverts besonders bunt und vielf&auml;ltig w&uuml;rde. Briefmarken waren f&uuml;r ihn Botschafter eines Landes und seiner Kultur, seiner Landschaft und Eigenart.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black&quot;&gt;Hundertwasser wurde eingeladen, Briefmarken f&uuml;r &Ouml;sterreich, f&uuml;r Senegal, die&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt; Vereinten Nationen,&lt;span style=&quot;color: black&quot;&gt; das F&uuml;rstentum Liechtenstein, f&uuml;r Luxemburg und andere L&auml;nder zu gestalten. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; color: black&quot;&gt;Hundertwassers Briefmarken stellen seit Jahren begehrte und gesuchte Objekte f&uuml;r Sammler dar.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Hundertwasser Archiv',
text_orig_lang-'',
