3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;The big curve flag - the Uluru&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;symbolizes the love of all Australians&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;for their grand, unique and magnificent nation,&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;in harmony with Australian traditions&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;The island continent down under&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;situated above the southern sky&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;the big curve&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Uluru, the red Ayers Rock&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;and the enormous shared commitment&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;to the earth and to humanity:&lt;p&gt;&