&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;because it is a constellation for all of the southern hemisphere including Chile, Argentina, Brazil, South Africa, Bolivia, Paraguay, Peru, Angola, Namibia, Madagascar, Mozambique, Zambia, Rhodesia, Botswana, Seychelles, Fiji, Samoa, Tonga, Tahiti and New Zealand.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;Australia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&#039;s flag must be original&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;and basically different from that of other nations.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;Australia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&#039;s flag cannot be merely the result&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;of a sterile and cold graphic design.&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;Australia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&#039;s flag must be inherent&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;to the identity, trust, life and love&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&g