]).

%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.4.5.1
object(text,'1.4.5.1','TO JOIN THE E.U. IS TO BETRAY AUSTRIA AND BETRAY EUROPE. WHY?',[
id-130,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-130,
txt-'1.4.5.1',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'TO JOIN THE E.U. IS TO BETRAY AUSTRIA AND BETRAY EUROPE. WHY?',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1994-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U. question the Austrian public is being subjected to a dogmatic brain washing by the state-controlled media the likes &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;of which has never been seen. Television, radio and almost the entire press are in the grip of a disgraceful veiled censorship.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I would also not think it possible in a democracy, if I hadn&rsquo;t experienced this kind of censorship myself. More than once all manner of pretexts and excuses were made to obstruct and prevent me from stating an anti-E.U. opinion publicly.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The excuses were: it has no relevance to the broadcast; I may not deliver a prepared text; it was not my responsibility; I was crazy; or they resorted to deliberate diffamation to destroy my credibility.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;And at that, my misgivings and fears have long since been corroborated in the E.U. states themselves. Why don&rsquo;t people listen to Leopold Kohr (&ldquo;The Breakdown of Nations&rdquo;), Ernst Friedrich Schumacher (&ldquo;Small is Beautiful&rdquo;), Jimmy Goldsmith (&ldquo;The Trap &ndash; and What If We Have Taken a Bad Road?&rdquo;), Henry Coston (&ldquo;The Europe of the Bankers&rdquo;), Jean-Pierre Chev&egrave;nement, Margaret Thatcher, Philippe S&eacute;guin, Marie-France Garaud, Elisabeth Guigou, Alberto Miele (&ldquo;Let&rsquo;s Drive the Merchants Out of the Temple of Europe&rdquo;), G&eacute;rard de Selys, Dr. Manfred Brunner (Anti-Maastricht Party), Sir Ralf Dahrendorf (ex-E.U. commissioner: &ldquo;Artificial super-construction not viable&rdquo;), Denis de Rougemont (&ldquo;Europe must strive for diversity&rdquo;) and untold other warning voices?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria has been chosen by history to be an example and centre and mainstay in Central Europe. Austria is a bridge of hope towards the East.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Since the war we have built up with laborious toil a huge capital of prosperity, domestic peace, international respect and credibility as an independent, attractive, peace-loving, cultivated nation in the heart of Europe. That cannot be shortsightedly and irresponsibly put at risk.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;At this very moment, after the collapse of the communist dictatorship and the opening of boundaries, Austria must be mindful of its responsibility in Europe and may not eliminate itself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;With a suggested last-minute panic, an &ldquo;Anschluss&rdquo; neurosis is being generated. Fear of what or whom? What enemies does Austria have? Who would jeopardise Austria&rsquo;s security, and why? Precisely by joining a military block, Austria would, as a &ldquo;fringe region East Mark&rdquo;, first be an area for marshalling forces and then become an enemy and target of attack (warning by Erwin Lanc). There is no cure for the threat of nuclear attack, and in regional wars &ndash; see Bosnia &ndash; there is no E.U. protection, not even in Northern Ireland, inside the E.U. itself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria&rsquo;s neutrality is at this precise moment more necessary than ever before. One must call neutrality by its real name and stand up for it. Neutrality is a true value. Permanent neutrality is the foundation of our state and must not be betrayed and eroded. If we undermine this foundation, we will destroy this our state, Austria, which has been erected upon it.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As of now Austria&rsquo;s neutrality means autonomy, independence, freedom, assuming responsibility, setting an example &ndash; an active neutrality.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Here, too, Switzerland is an example and is also cited as an example in the [Austrian] State Treaty.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There is no reason for cutting a divide right across Europe at this of all moments. It is as if to the east of Vienna were enemy territory. &lt;em&gt;Border patrols are being deployed by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Germany&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; right where the Iron Curtain has just been removed!&lt;/em&gt; This new line of demarcation runs not only right through Europe, but right through Austria, where the Danube monarchy was. It would be irresponsible and dangerous to increase the difference with and the threat to the countries &ldquo;on the outside&rdquo; by an Anschluss with an economically and politically superior power. Austria&rsquo;s cultural, economic and historic destiny, Austria&rsquo;s responsibility and its appeal lie to the East.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is also what the name Austria &ndash; &Ouml;sterreich in German &ndash; really means: realm to the east.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The fronts have undergone a change. It is no longer the political boundaries, the front is now drawn between the brutal throw-away society, which is only interested in business, and exploited nature and the destroyed soul of man.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There is a new resistance, and already there are once again cowardly collaborators.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The politicians who now bear the responsibility are puppets of business interests and pay hypocritical lip service to environmental awareness and cultural consciousness. They adopt measures which destroy the environment and culture and make our future doubtful.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The so-called E.U. is contriving to destroy our life base, our ageold cultures, our small, evolved idiosyncrasies, our species diversity and our self-esteem.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. is a gigantic sales outlet of big business, the labour unions, the trade associations, the major banks, the poison corporations, the monoculture monopolists and the nuclear and genetic lobbies, which are about to load us like meek sheep onto a train going in the wrong direction, together with the cattle for slaughter.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This huge business mafia is interested solely in power and money and not in the well-being of nature and man. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Remote-controlled, gigantic misguided planning by irresponsible strategists sitting at their desks is destroying the foundations of our Europe, which have taken ages to grow.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Europe is undergoing the grossest rape in its history.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;From Brussels no spiritual and cultural renewal of Europe will come. From there come no answers to the questions occupying the conscience of the peoples of Europe (Alberto Miele).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;From this new hegemony no messages come regarding the identity, our age-old values, the substance of our civilisation and the longings of the people of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Where are the cultures, the religions, the philosophies to launch a new European epoch?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Precisely now, when our society is reaching the limits of growth, decentralisation is our only chance of survival.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;An Anschluss with this overpowering central authority, which, despite all evidence to the contrary, still intends to push economic growth through as its central dogma, will have catastrophic consequences for all concerned.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What this E.U. is trying to draw us into is a merciless competitive struggle, to make us run amok in a great, dangerous illusion, in the cul-de-sac of economic growth. It would be madness to join this exclusive club of throw-away society which is throwing itself into the dustbin and reducing itself to absurdity.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If the E.U. is such a good product, why do they have to promote it so intensively? And this suspicious pressure: we must dispossess ourselves immediately or it will be too late! All good things happen slowly, in an organic process, of themselves. A tree cannot be convinced and persuaded even by threats to blossom in the middle of winter.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I do not understand why they want at all costs to persuade us to board the E.U., this sinking ship, right away.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. is a gigantic Titanic. The analogies to the sinking of the Titanic are horrifying. In both cases lack of planning, megalomania, immoderation, blind faith in technology and the mania of speed at all costs. If the former raced for the Blue Ribbon through the deadly icebergs, the latter is in a murderous race to the limits of growth of the throw-away society which is destroying our environment and us.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One should not board such a &ldquo;doomed steamer Europe&rdquo; and entrust it with our life and future. Better to stay in a small but maneuverable boat.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Just about everywhere in the E.U. things are out of control: Northern Ireland, the Basque region, Corsica, the Mafia, Camorra, persecution of foreigners, racial hatred and pogroms, discrimination against Greenlanders, Macedonians and the Bretons, brutal strikes, bloody excesses, student revolts, drug crime, nuclear-plant mishaps, devastated tracts of land, apathy and a feeling of looming disaster, juvenile crime, soon 20 million out of work and a split-up of the country into Flemish and Walloons, in Brussels, of all places, the seat of the European Union. Compared to this, &ldquo;isolated Austria&rdquo; and the Scandinavian countries, whom they want to herd into the E.U. at all costs, are pretty well off &ldquo;on the outside&rdquo;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U. human fates are juggled like pawns [called &ldquo;farmers&rdquo; in German] on a chessboard. But you can&rsquo;t fob off free farmers with money and send them off to their allotted property, that is humiliating, or use them as folklore and alibi farmers, to be trotted out for the tourists; that goes against honour and self-respect; that is worse than murder.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;They are paying the farmers for their suicide. The E.U. is demanding that the farmers destroy their age-old culture. For this they will receive money. In contrast to disaster relief, the disaster is first made to happen on purpose. Evolved structures cannot be compensated for even with a great deal of money once they have been done away with. You can&rsquo;t raise the dead with money.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A few powerful and competitive industrial magnates favour membership in the E.U. in order to gain even more economic advantage. But that will happen at the cost of small business and small farmers, which are jeopardised as it is.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I know from my own experience that in the E.U. countries, in France, for example, only agrarian co-operatives with over 100 hectares have a chance of survival.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This is then how it will look: either barren fields lying fallow, deserted villages or the levelling of terrain, the removal of copses, trees and rocks which get in the way of large machines, the razing of ancient farmsteads, the regulation of brooks. Perfidious destruction, with gigantic repercussions in excess of any war.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The increased use of artificial fertilizer, pesticides, genetic manipulation, radiation and environmental toxins of all kinds, of course manufactured in the E.U. A sadistic, technocratic destruction of any kind of romanticism with the catchword &ldquo;unprofitable&rdquo;. Monoculture as far as the eye can see. The farmer is advised to systematically violate the basis of our survival, to poison and destroy the soil, forests and meadows entrusted to his care. Agriculture will then become a gigantic agribusiness industry.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The dependence of farmers and of all of us on industry, chemistry and monopolistic businesses, this new serfdom, will be increased to an intolerable level by joining the E.U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Foreign, more powerful, more brutal commanders take the place of the smaller domestic companies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This will also be the fate of the smaller, i. e., all human business operations: they will be destroyed; instead, there will be more large department stores, large banks and large-scale industrialisation. In short, everything which makes our life romantic, attractive and worth living will scarcely have a way of surviving. Stupid brutality will be victorious; the delicate values will perish because they can&rsquo;t defend themselves.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Agribusiness in the E.U. practises, in a close analogy to the Third Reich, a brutal selection process of pure-blooded, conformist &ldquo;elite&rdquo; products and the elimination of &ldquo;inferior&rdquo; genotypes or seeds.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This begins with the nice big apples which all have to be alike, which are bred in monocultures, of the same &ldquo;race&rdquo;, with the same taste, and is continued with genetic &ldquo;improvement of economic animals&rdquo; and the batteries of laying hens. Any unproductive life is eliminated. All unprofitable diversity, everything which is different, everything small-scale, all useless species diversity, all unprofitable beauty, are destroyed.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This makes the small farm die, too, the family farms, romanticism: in short, our quality of life.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The dying-out of the mom-and-pop stores, the farmers, family farms and small businesses, the death of small entities brings about a conformism and anonymisation of our society. Man is robbed of his dignity. This creates a new dependence, a new enslavement, a new serfdom on an unheard-of scale.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is the end of humanistic Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What then remains is a world not fitting to man, but a machine-compatible, computer-compatible one. It is a destruction of higher values which in their diversity are what make Europe what it is. It is the destruction of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The small farmers must sell their houses, their barnyards, their land; they are then either unemployed or join the urban proletariat or must join agribusiness co-operatives, where they merely take orders, with no freedom to decide for themselves, on land which once belonged to them.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The E.U. is plagued by a growing army of unemployed, which even now amounts to the working population of a country 7 to 10 times as big as Austria!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One can imagine what a devastating example the E.U. is setting for the world if the three thousand million people who are eking out an existence on the land in the Third World are forced to follow this E.U. example.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A gigantic deluge of refugees, two thousand million people from rural areas &ndash; this &ldquo;global rural exodus&rdquo;, as Jimmy Goldsmith warns &ndash; would be more than the world can cope with.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Boundaries are like our skin. They protect the grown organism, our individual differentness, from danger from the outside, such as heat and cold. If the skin is removed, the organism dies because it has no protection. &lt;em&gt;That is why we have protective tariffs to protect an endangered polity. Like the way we use sunglasses and vaccinations against Lyme&rsquo;s disease etc., for our protection.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What God has separated we should not unite by force.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There are natural boundaries, e.g., the Sahara, the Mediterranean and the Alps, under whose protection age-old cultures have evolved, such as the African, the Mediterranean and the Northern European cultures. The Alps have a protective function for the North as well as the South.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Unencumbered, senseless transit traffic is tantamount to tearing down and levelling off the Alps, even if the traffic is routed through tunnels. Austria has a function as an Alpine protective sentry for Europe, just like Switzerland.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This feverish, unnatural, mindless racing back and forth is madness and becomes in the E.U. &ldquo;madness unlimited&rdquo;. Wherever we happen to be, we ruin everything; then we flee from our own destruction, only to ruin everything somewhere else, and on the way there everything is destroyed, too. This false trend is encouraged and supported in the E.U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Elisabeth Guigou puts it this way: an economy which is only geared to short-term profitability, without planning, without vision, without meaning, which produces labour-devouring machines, which is more and more dependent on the speed of communication and which with no regard to ecological balance forces people to an equally forced mobility, like its goods, capital, technologies and information, in contempt of human dignity and protection of the accustomed way of living, [is] an economic dictatorship which triumphs over all human activity &hellip;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If you kill what you are supposed to protect beforehand, you don&rsquo;t need to protect it anymore. First the farmers and mom-and-pop shops have to go and the small businesses and &ldquo;useless&rdquo; species diversity, &ldquo;unprofitable&rdquo; variety. First we must adapt to international mediocrity, to poisoned food, genetically engineered and irradiated foodstuffs. First, in our haste to obey, we must reduce ourselves to the lowest common denominator and annihilate ourselves; then the E.U. can march in unresisted and march right through.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria as a whole will become a vassal state, a new Ostmark. Needless to say, Austria&rsquo;s position as a neutral, environmentally conscious nation free of nuclear power will scarcely be tenable any longer. Then Austria will no longer be able to decide what it wants to do for itself, what and how much it produces and to which countries it will export and from which it will import goods. Austria&rsquo;s fortunes will be decided by strangers in Brussels or elsewhere in the E.U., by strategists sitting at their desks who don&rsquo;t care a fig about Austria&rsquo;s autonomy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria&rsquo;s wish for neutrality, Austria&rsquo;s environmental awareness will only be a source of mirth in the E.U. command centre.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The slogan &ldquo;alone or together&rdquo; is an alarmist, demagogical appeal to insecurity, to servitude and dependence. It may sound paradoxical, but anyone is strongest when he is alone. I know from personal experience that a person standing alone is just as strong as the group; he is not weaker. The man on the outside is more mobile, more effective in his action and reaction than a cumbersome, bureaucratic, chaotic organisation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Europe is only strong thanks to the diversity of its autonomies. This small-scale diversity must be bolstered and protected. This diversity is Europe. De Gaulle already realised that Europe only has a chance as a Europe of independent, free fatherlands.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is incomprehensible how irresponsibly our politicians now intend to relinquish our most valuable asset, our independence, freedom and autonomy and declare Austria legally incapacitated.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is a betrayal of Austria.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The last time there was an Anschluss there were any number of Seyss-Inquarts, Quislings, P&eacute;tains, too, who in their situation at the time probably also thought that their convictions and patriotism were making them do the right thing, that they were doing their duty by entrusting their country to foreign hegemony.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Today history teaches us that their actions were wrong and harmful, and they have long since been branded, punished and executed as traitors and collaborators.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cling together &ndash; swing together.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Beneath the smokescreen of the E.U. the Anschluss is taking place, unnoticed by everyone. When this E.U. then founders, we will have lost one more piece of our independence and will be stuck to our German big brother.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;While bearing all the differences in mind, Austria already experienced a similar fate when, in 1937&ndash;1938, an Anschluss to the &ldquo;Old Reich&rdquo; was propageted, also for economic reasons. &ldquo;Back home to the Reich&rdquo; was the slogan then.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The exchange of the schilling to the superpower-Euro brings ominous analogies with the exchange of the schilling to the Reichmark in 1938 to mind.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It must not be forgotten that the promise of financial and economic improvement for the future population of the East Mark was the main reason that many Austrians intended to vote for the Anschluss.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The acclaimed integration with Greater Germany was followed by disenchantment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Now it is similar. Precisely what they are touting in the E.U. is what we will lose in the E.U.: social prosperity, full employment, an intact environment, our high quality of life, our homeland, our self-esteem, our nature and our age-old cultures.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One is only a European if one retains and values one&rsquo;s independent, autonomous European-ness. Switzerland, prosperous and democratic, also located in the heart of Europe, should be a shining example to us.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I also don&rsquo;t understand why our Federal President is urging us to give up our sovereignty. After all, he, our highest-ranking patriot, should be issuing a warning and protecting our constitution. Is treason not a crime, the intention to subject Austria to a foreign central authority?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The State Treaty brought liberation to Austria. The E.U. Treaty is a capitulation by Austria, a legal incapacitation of Austria, a subjugation to a new, anachronistic hegemony &ndash; and a breach of the State Treaty.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is incredible: the politicians are preparing for a second Anschluss and want to present a fait accompli to the Austrian people. Are our politicians out of their minds, so that only history can show them the error of their ways?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am not a lawyer, but I am firmly convinced that we are being manipulated by powerful interest groups which are outside the pale of any ethical, historical, moral, cultural and ecological legality with a despicable demagogy, just like with Zwentendorf back then &lt;em&gt;(the beginning of operations at the nuclear power plant was prevented by a plebiscite)&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The E.U. countries are being reduced to the lowest common denominator, rendered anonymous and robbed of their identity. That is the direction this is moving in and not in the direction of decentralisation &lt;em&gt;and the deepening&lt;/em&gt; of autonomies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As proof, just take the E.U. flag with, as of now, 12 five-pointed little stars exactly alike. Which of these stars would stand for Austria, the one third on the right from the bottom, maybe, or the second, which looks exactly the same?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The five-pointed star is not a symbol from European history, and certainly not from Austria&rsquo;s. In the evolution of the states of the Occident it does not occur. The pentagram, an occult symbol of the Druids and Free Masons, is a foreign body to western heraldry.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The five-pointed star serves rather as a sign of subjugation, conquest and colonisation, as on the flags of Australia, New Zealand, America and diverse colonial regimes.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. flag is in addition a plagiarised version of the Stars and Stripes. The United States of America were also arranged as five-pointed stars, white on blue, at first in a circle, just like the would-be &ldquo;United States of Europe&rdquo;. Later, when there were more of them, they were brought into rank and file.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;These little five-pointed stars are just like the Soviet star, the star of the Yugoslavian, Chinese, Cuban and the other people&rsquo;s epublics. Indeed, this symbol is pathetic proof of the evolved identities of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is a bad omen when even the symbol is wrong. This E.U. flag of stars symbolises Europe&rsquo;s self-sacrifice.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the so-called E.U. culture is less than a secondary matter. Creative talents are being trimmed down to useful idiots. To support and window-dress and legitimise a mercantile and industrial growth which is self-destructive.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Culture is not present in Brussels. It is not relevant in the solely mercantile and industrial E.U. In Brussels they know the price of everything and the value of nothing.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In this culture-devoid so-called E.U. only numbers count: production figures, deadlines and terms, transition times, population and cattle statistics. Gross national product, agricultural, forest and pastures in square kilometers, labour costs, social benefits, ancillary costs. Export figures, tonnage of heavy transport, milk prices, price adjustments, financing figures, compensatory figures, percents, price reductions, sugar, milk and fish quotas, transit restrictions in numbers, contingents, co-financing, tables, statistics, market-access restrictions in figures. Terms of validity, ecu exchange rates, high unemployment figures, low employment figures, subsidy figures, the number of eco-points, monetary remittances of all kinds, irreal figures on economic growth, poll results in numbers and percents, number of votes in the Council of Ministers and of the blocking minority, majorities, minorities, voting results, E.U. advertising expenditures. Even altitude statistics for alpine famers in meters and latitudes for agriculture in Finland.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If that is not symptomatic!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Environmental protection is also absent in the Brussels hegemony. Only 0.3 percent of the E.U. officials (30 out of 10,000) are concerned with ecology. Talk of environmental protection across borders is just that. Austria must share in the financing of nuclear energy and admit, e.g., plastic bottles and &lt;em&gt;genetically engineered products&lt;/em&gt; and idiotically dangerous regulations on the size of apples and monoculture fruit varieties. I have seen this myself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In Brussels nobody speaks of culture and Western values. Brussels only makes expenditures for culture when asked to. Cultural studies, indeed all study courses, are oriented in the E.U. to their usefulness for industry and to exaggerated growth goals.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Only creation can teach us creativity and organic growth. Only creation can teach us to respect species diversity and its incredibly rich variety, of which we are a part ourselves.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U., however, efforts are being made in precisely the opposite direction: destruction of the small-scale, creative values in favour of a completely false and outdated automatisation, centralisation and rationalisation, which will be our ruin sooner or later.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The conscience of our civilisation, our age-old destiny to strive for higher values, is being left behind.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U. question the Austrian public is being subjected to a dogmatic brain washing by the state-controlled media the likes &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;of which has never been seen. Television, radio and almost the entire press are in the grip of a disgraceful veiled censorship.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I would also not think it possible in a democracy, if I hadn&rsquo;t experienced this kind of censorship myself. More than once all manner of pretexts and excuses were made to obstruct and prevent me from stating an anti-E.U. opinion publicly.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The excuses were: it has no relevance to the broadcast; I may not deliver a prepared text; it was not my responsibility; I was crazy; or they resorted to deliberate diffamation to destroy my credibility.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;And at that, my misgivings and fears have long since been corroborated in the E.U. states themselves. Why don&rsquo;t people listen to Leopold Kohr (&ldquo;The Breakdown of Nations&rdquo;), Ernst Friedrich Schumacher (&ldquo;Small is Beautiful&rdquo;), Jimmy Goldsmith (&ldquo;The Trap &ndash; and What If We Have Taken a Bad Road?&rdquo;), Henry Coston (&ldquo;The Europe of the Bankers&rdquo;), Jean-Pierre Chev&egrave;nement, Margaret Thatcher, Philippe S&eacute;guin, Marie-France Garaud, Elisabeth Guigou, Alberto Miele (&ldquo;Let&rsquo;s Drive the Merchants Out of the Temple of Europe&rdquo;), G&eacute;rard de Selys, Dr. Manfred Brunner (Anti-Maastricht Party), Sir Ralf Dahrendorf (ex-E.U. commissioner: &ldquo;Artificial super-construction not viable&rdquo;), Denis de Rougemont (&ldquo;Europe must strive for diversity&rdquo;) and untold other warning voices?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria has been chosen by history to be an example and centre and mainstay in Central Europe. Austria is a bridge of hope towards the East.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Since the war we have built up with laborious toil a huge capital of prosperity, domestic peace, international respect and credibility as an independent, attractive, peace-loving, cultivated nation in the heart of Europe. That cannot be shortsightedly and irresponsibly put at risk.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;At this very moment, after the collapse of the communist dictatorship and the opening of boundaries, Austria must be mindful of its responsibility in Europe and may not eliminate itself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;With a suggested last-minute panic, an &ldquo;Anschluss&rdquo; neurosis is being generated. Fear of what or whom? What enemies does Austria have? Who would jeopardise Austria&rsquo;s security, and why? Precisely by joining a military block, Austria would, as a &ldquo;fringe region East Mark&rdquo;, first be an area for marshalling forces and then become an enemy and target of attack (warning by Erwin Lanc). There is no cure for the threat of nuclear attack, and in regional wars &ndash; see Bosnia &ndash; there is no E.U. protection, not even in Northern Ireland, inside the E.U. itself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria&rsquo;s neutrality is at this precise moment more necessary than ever before. One must call neutrality by its real name and stand up for it. Neutrality is a true value. Permanent neutrality is the foundation of our state and must not be betrayed and eroded. If we undermine this foundation, we will destroy this our state, Austria, which has been erected upon it.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As of now Austria&rsquo;s neutrality means autonomy, independence, freedom, assuming responsibility, setting an example &ndash; an active neutrality.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Here, too, Switzerland is an example and is also cited as an example in the [Austrian] State Treaty.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There is no reason for cutting a divide right across Europe at this of all moments. It is as if to the east of Vienna were enemy territory. &lt;em&gt;Border patrols are being deployed by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Germany&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; right where the Iron Curtain has just been removed!&lt;/em&gt; This new line of demarcation runs not only right through Europe, but right through Austria, where the Danube monarchy was. It would be irresponsible and dangerous to increase the difference with and the threat to the countries &ldquo;on the outside&rdquo; by an Anschluss with an economically and politically superior power. Austria&rsquo;s cultural, economic and historic destiny, Austria&rsquo;s responsibility and its appeal lie to the East.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is also what the name Austria &ndash; &Ouml;sterreich in German &ndash; really means: realm to the east.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The fronts have undergone a change. It is no longer the political boundaries, the front is now drawn between the brutal throw-away society, which is only interested in business, and exploited nature and the destroyed soul of man.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There is a new resistance, and already there are once again cowardly collaborators.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The politicians who now bear the responsibility are puppets of business interests and pay hypocritical lip service to environmental awareness and cultural consciousness. They adopt measures which destroy the environment and culture and make our future doubtful.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The so-called E.U. is contriving to destroy our life base, our ageold cultures, our small, evolved idiosyncrasies, our species diversity and our self-esteem.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. is a gigantic sales outlet of big business, the labour unions, the trade associations, the major banks, the poison corporations, the monoculture monopolists and the nuclear and genetic lobbies, which are about to load us like meek sheep onto a train going in the wrong direction, together with the cattle for slaughter.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This huge business mafia is interested solely in power and money and not in the well-being of nature and man. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Remote-controlled, gigantic misguided planning by irresponsible strategists sitting at their desks is destroying the foundations of our Europe, which have taken ages to grow.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Europe is undergoing the grossest rape in its history.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;From Brussels no spiritual and cultural renewal of Europe will come. From there come no answers to the questions occupying the conscience of the peoples of Europe (Alberto Miele).&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;From this new hegemony no messages come regarding the identity, our age-old values, the substance of our civilisation and the longings of the people of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Where are the cultures, the religions, the philosophies to launch a new European epoch?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Precisely now, when our society is reaching the limits of growth, decentralisation is our only chance of survival.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;An Anschluss with this overpowering central authority, which, despite all evidence to the contrary, still intends to push economic growth through as its central dogma, will have catastrophic consequences for all concerned.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What this E.U. is trying to draw us into is a merciless competitive struggle, to make us run amok in a great, dangerous illusion, in the cul-de-sac of economic growth. It would be madness to join this exclusive club of throw-away society which is throwing itself into the dustbin and reducing itself to absurdity.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If the E.U. is such a good product, why do they have to promote it so intensively? And this suspicious pressure: we must dispossess ourselves immediately or it will be too late! All good things happen slowly, in an organic process, of themselves. A tree cannot be convinced and persuaded even by threats to blossom in the middle of winter.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I do not understand why they want at all costs to persuade us to board the E.U., this sinking ship, right away.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. is a gigantic Titanic. The analogies to the sinking of the Titanic are horrifying. In both cases lack of planning, megalomania, immoderation, blind faith in technology and the mania of speed at all costs. If the former raced for the Blue Ribbon through the deadly icebergs, the latter is in a murderous race to the limits of growth of the throw-away society which is destroying our environment and us.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One should not board such a &ldquo;doomed steamer Europe&rdquo; and entrust it with our life and future. Better to stay in a small but maneuverable boat.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Just about everywhere in the E.U. things are out of control: Northern Ireland, the Basque region, Corsica, the Mafia, Camorra, persecution of foreigners, racial hatred and pogroms, discrimination against Greenlanders, Macedonians and the Bretons, brutal strikes, bloody excesses, student revolts, drug crime, nuclear-plant mishaps, devastated tracts of land, apathy and a feeling of looming disaster, juvenile crime, soon 20 million out of work and a split-up of the country into Flemish and Walloons, in Brussels, of all places, the seat of the European Union. Compared to this, &ldquo;isolated Austria&rdquo; and the Scandinavian countries, whom they want to herd into the E.U. at all costs, are pretty well off &ldquo;on the outside&rdquo;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U. human fates are juggled like pawns [called &ldquo;farmers&rdquo; in German] on a chessboard. But you can&rsquo;t fob off free farmers with money and send them off to their allotted property, that is humiliating, or use them as folklore and alibi farmers, to be trotted out for the tourists; that goes against honour and self-respect; that is worse than murder.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;They are paying the farmers for their suicide. The E.U. is demanding that the farmers destroy their age-old culture. For this they will receive money. In contrast to disaster relief, the disaster is first made to happen on purpose. Evolved structures cannot be compensated for even with a great deal of money once they have been done away with. You can&rsquo;t raise the dead with money.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A few powerful and competitive industrial magnates favour membership in the E.U. in order to gain even more economic advantage. But that will happen at the cost of small business and small farmers, which are jeopardised as it is.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I know from my own experience that in the E.U. countries, in France, for example, only agrarian co-operatives with over 100 hectares have a chance of survival.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This is then how it will look: either barren fields lying fallow, deserted villages or the levelling of terrain, the removal of copses, trees and rocks which get in the way of large machines, the razing of ancient farmsteads, the regulation of brooks. Perfidious destruction, with gigantic repercussions in excess of any war.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The increased use of artificial fertilizer, pesticides, genetic manipulation, radiation and environmental toxins of all kinds, of course manufactured in the E.U. A sadistic, technocratic destruction of any kind of romanticism with the catchword &ldquo;unprofitable&rdquo;. Monoculture as far as the eye can see. The farmer is advised to systematically violate the basis of our survival, to poison and destroy the soil, forests and meadows entrusted to his care. Agriculture will then become a gigantic agribusiness industry.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The dependence of farmers and of all of us on industry, chemistry and monopolistic businesses, this new serfdom, will be increased to an intolerable level by joining the E.U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Foreign, more powerful, more brutal commanders take the place of the smaller domestic companies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This will also be the fate of the smaller, i. e., all human business operations: they will be destroyed; instead, there will be more large department stores, large banks and large-scale industrialisation. In short, everything which makes our life romantic, attractive and worth living will scarcely have a way of surviving. Stupid brutality will be victorious; the delicate values will perish because they can&rsquo;t defend themselves.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Agribusiness in the E.U. practises, in a close analogy to the Third Reich, a brutal selection process of pure-blooded, conformist &ldquo;elite&rdquo; products and the elimination of &ldquo;inferior&rdquo; genotypes or seeds.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This begins with the nice big apples which all have to be alike, which are bred in monocultures, of the same &ldquo;race&rdquo;, with the same taste, and is continued with genetic &ldquo;improvement of economic animals&rdquo; and the batteries of laying hens. Any unproductive life is eliminated. All unprofitable diversity, everything which is different, everything small-scale, all useless species diversity, all unprofitable beauty, are destroyed.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This makes the small farm die, too, the family farms, romanticism: in short, our quality of life.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The dying-out of the mom-and-pop stores, the farmers, family farms and small businesses, the death of small entities brings about a conformism and anonymisation of our society. Man is robbed of his dignity. This creates a new dependence, a new enslavement, a new serfdom on an unheard-of scale.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is the end of humanistic Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What then remains is a world not fitting to man, but a machine-compatible, computer-compatible one. It is a destruction of higher values which in their diversity are what make Europe what it is. It is the destruction of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The small farmers must sell their houses, their barnyards, their land; they are then either unemployed or join the urban proletariat or must join agribusiness co-operatives, where they merely take orders, with no freedom to decide for themselves, on land which once belonged to them.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The E.U. is plagued by a growing army of unemployed, which even now amounts to the working population of a country 7 to 10 times as big as Austria!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One can imagine what a devastating example the E.U. is setting for the world if the three thousand million people who are eking out an existence on the land in the Third World are forced to follow this E.U. example.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;A gigantic deluge of refugees, two thousand million people from rural areas &ndash; this &ldquo;global rural exodus&rdquo;, as Jimmy Goldsmith warns &ndash; would be more than the world can cope with.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Boundaries are like our skin. They protect the grown organism, our individual differentness, from danger from the outside, such as heat and cold. If the skin is removed, the organism dies because it has no protection. &lt;em&gt;That is why we have protective tariffs to protect an endangered polity. Like the way we use sunglasses and vaccinations against Lyme&rsquo;s disease etc., for our protection.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;What God has separated we should not unite by force.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;There are natural boundaries, e.g., the Sahara, the Mediterranean and the Alps, under whose protection age-old cultures have evolved, such as the African, the Mediterranean and the Northern European cultures. The Alps have a protective function for the North as well as the South.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Unencumbered, senseless transit traffic is tantamount to tearing down and levelling off the Alps, even if the traffic is routed through tunnels. Austria has a function as an Alpine protective sentry for Europe, just like Switzerland.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This feverish, unnatural, mindless racing back and forth is madness and becomes in the E.U. &ldquo;madness unlimited&rdquo;. Wherever we happen to be, we ruin everything; then we flee from our own destruction, only to ruin everything somewhere else, and on the way there everything is destroyed, too. This false trend is encouraged and supported in the E.U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Elisabeth Guigou puts it this way: an economy which is only geared to short-term profitability, without planning, without vision, without meaning, which produces labour-devouring machines, which is more and more dependent on the speed of communication and which with no regard to ecological balance forces people to an equally forced mobility, like its goods, capital, technologies and information, in contempt of human dignity and protection of the accustomed way of living, [is] an economic dictatorship which triumphs over all human activity &hellip;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If you kill what you are supposed to protect beforehand, you don&rsquo;t need to protect it anymore. First the farmers and mom-and-pop shops have to go and the small businesses and &ldquo;useless&rdquo; species diversity, &ldquo;unprofitable&rdquo; variety. First we must adapt to international mediocrity, to poisoned food, genetically engineered and irradiated foodstuffs. First, in our haste to obey, we must reduce ourselves to the lowest common denominator and annihilate ourselves; then the E.U. can march in unresisted and march right through.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria as a whole will become a vassal state, a new Ostmark. Needless to say, Austria&rsquo;s position as a neutral, environmentally conscious nation free of nuclear power will scarcely be tenable any longer. Then Austria will no longer be able to decide what it wants to do for itself, what and how much it produces and to which countries it will export and from which it will import goods. Austria&rsquo;s fortunes will be decided by strangers in Brussels or elsewhere in the E.U., by strategists sitting at their desks who don&rsquo;t care a fig about Austria&rsquo;s autonomy.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Austria&rsquo;s wish for neutrality, Austria&rsquo;s environmental awareness will only be a source of mirth in the E.U. command centre.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The slogan &ldquo;alone or together&rdquo; is an alarmist, demagogical appeal to insecurity, to servitude and dependence. It may sound paradoxical, but anyone is strongest when he is alone. I know from personal experience that a person standing alone is just as strong as the group; he is not weaker. The man on the outside is more mobile, more effective in his action and reaction than a cumbersome, bureaucratic, chaotic organisation.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Europe is only strong thanks to the diversity of its autonomies. This small-scale diversity must be bolstered and protected. This diversity is Europe. De Gaulle already realised that Europe only has a chance as a Europe of independent, free fatherlands.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is incomprehensible how irresponsibly our politicians now intend to relinquish our most valuable asset, our independence, freedom and autonomy and declare Austria legally incapacitated.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;That is a betrayal of Austria.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The last time there was an Anschluss there were any number of Seyss-Inquarts, Quislings, P&eacute;tains, too, who in their situation at the time probably also thought that their convictions and patriotism were making them do the right thing, that they were doing their duty by entrusting their country to foreign hegemony.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Today history teaches us that their actions were wrong and harmful, and they have long since been branded, punished and executed as traitors and collaborators.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Cling together &ndash; swing together.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Beneath the smokescreen of the E.U. the Anschluss is taking place, unnoticed by everyone. When this E.U. then founders, we will have lost one more piece of our independence and will be stuck to our German big brother.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;While bearing all the differences in mind, Austria already experienced a similar fate when, in 1937&ndash;1938, an Anschluss to the &ldquo;Old Reich&rdquo; was propageted, also for economic reasons. &ldquo;Back home to the Reich&rdquo; was the slogan then.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The exchange of the schilling to the superpower-Euro brings ominous analogies with the exchange of the schilling to the Reichmark in 1938 to mind.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It must not be forgotten that the promise of financial and economic improvement for the future population of the East Mark was the main reason that many Austrians intended to vote for the Anschluss.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The acclaimed integration with Greater Germany was followed by disenchantment.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Now it is similar. Precisely what they are touting in the E.U. is what we will lose in the E.U.: social prosperity, full employment, an intact environment, our high quality of life, our homeland, our self-esteem, our nature and our age-old cultures.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;One is only a European if one retains and values one&rsquo;s independent, autonomous European-ness. Switzerland, prosperous and democratic, also located in the heart of Europe, should be a shining example to us.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I also don&rsquo;t understand why our Federal President is urging us to give up our sovereignty. After all, he, our highest-ranking patriot, should be issuing a warning and protecting our constitution. Is treason not a crime, the intention to subject Austria to a foreign central authority?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The State Treaty brought liberation to Austria. The E.U. Treaty is a capitulation by Austria, a legal incapacitation of Austria, a subjugation to a new, anachronistic hegemony &ndash; and a breach of the State Treaty.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is incredible: the politicians are preparing for a second Anschluss and want to present a fait accompli to the Austrian people. Are our politicians out of their minds, so that only history can show them the error of their ways?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;I am not a lawyer, but I am firmly convinced that we are being manipulated by powerful interest groups which are outside the pale of any ethical, historical, moral, cultural and ecological legality with a despicable demagogy, just like with Zwentendorf back then &lt;em&gt;(the beginning of operations at the nuclear power plant was prevented by a plebiscite)&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The E.U. countries are being reduced to the lowest common denominator, rendered anonymous and robbed of their identity. That is the direction this is moving in and not in the direction of decentralisation &lt;em&gt;and the deepening&lt;/em&gt; of autonomies.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As proof, just take the E.U. flag with, as of now, 12 five-pointed little stars exactly alike. Which of these stars would stand for Austria, the one third on the right from the bottom, maybe, or the second, which looks exactly the same?&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The five-pointed star is not a symbol from European history, and certainly not from Austria&rsquo;s. In the evolution of the states of the Occident it does not occur. The pentagram, an occult symbol of the Druids and Free Masons, is a foreign body to western heraldry.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The five-pointed star serves rather as a sign of subjugation, conquest and colonisation, as on the flags of Australia, New Zealand, America and diverse colonial regimes.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;This E.U. flag is in addition a plagiarised version of the Stars and Stripes. The United States of America were also arranged as five-pointed stars, white on blue, at first in a circle, just like the would-be &ldquo;United States of Europe&rdquo;. Later, when there were more of them, they were brought into rank and file.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;These little five-pointed stars are just like the Soviet star, the star of the Yugoslavian, Chinese, Cuban and the other people&rsquo;s epublics. Indeed, this symbol is pathetic proof of the evolved identities of Europe.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;It is a bad omen when even the symbol is wrong. This E.U. flag of stars symbolises Europe&rsquo;s self-sacrifice.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the so-called E.U. culture is less than a secondary matter. Creative talents are being trimmed down to useful idiots. To support and window-dress and legitimise a mercantile and industrial growth which is self-destructive.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Culture is not present in Brussels. It is not relevant in the solely mercantile and industrial E.U. In Brussels they know the price of everything and the value of nothing.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In this culture-devoid so-called E.U. only numbers count: production figures, deadlines and terms, transition times, population and cattle statistics. Gross national product, agricultural, forest and pastures in square kilometers, labour costs, social benefits, ancillary costs. Export figures, tonnage of heavy transport, milk prices, price adjustments, financing figures, compensatory figures, percents, price reductions, sugar, milk and fish quotas, transit restrictions in numbers, contingents, co-financing, tables, statistics, market-access restrictions in figures. Terms of validity, ecu exchange rates, high unemployment figures, low employment figures, subsidy figures, the number of eco-points, monetary remittances of all kinds, irreal figures on economic growth, poll results in numbers and percents, number of votes in the Council of Ministers and of the blocking minority, majorities, minorities, voting results, E.U. advertising expenditures. Even altitude statistics for alpine famers in meters and latitudes for agriculture in Finland.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;If that is not symptomatic!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Environmental protection is also absent in the Brussels hegemony. Only 0.3 percent of the E.U. officials (30 out of 10,000) are concerned with ecology. Talk of environmental protection across borders is just that. Austria must share in the financing of nuclear energy and admit, e.g., plastic bottles and &lt;em&gt;genetically engineered products&lt;/em&gt; and idiotically dangerous regulations on the size of apples and monoculture fruit varieties. I have seen this myself.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In Brussels nobody speaks of culture and Western values. Brussels only makes expenditures for culture when asked to. Cultural studies, indeed all study courses, are oriented in the E.U. to their usefulness for industry and to exaggerated growth goals.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Only creation can teach us creativity and organic growth. Only creation can teach us to respect species diversity and its incredibly rich variety, of which we are a part ourselves.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;In the E.U., however, efforts are being made in precisely the opposite direction: destruction of the small-scale, creative values in favour of a completely false and outdated automatisation, centralisation and rationalisation, which will be our ruin sooner or later.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;The conscience of our civilisation, our age-old destiny to strive for higher values, is being left behind.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;In Sache &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; wird die &ouml;sterreichische &Ouml;ffentlichkeit von den staatlichen Medien einer dogmatischen Gehirnw&auml;sche ohnegleichen ausgesetzt. Es herrscht im Fernsehen, im Radio und fast in der gesamten Presse eine infame verschleierte Zensur.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ich w&uuml;rde das auch nicht in einer Demokratie f&uuml;r m&ouml;glich halten, h&auml;tte ich diese Art von Zensur nicht selbst erlebt. Unter allerlei Pr&auml;texten und Vorw&auml;nden wurde ich mehrmals behindert und verhindert,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; &ouml;ffentlich&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; eine Anti-&lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Meinung zu vertreten. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Vorw&auml;nde waren: es passe nicht in die Sendung, ich d&uuml;rfe nichts vorlesen, ich w&auml;re daf&uuml;r nicht zust&auml;ndig, ich w&auml;re verr&uuml;ckt oder aber man versucht mit gezielter Diffamation mich unglaubw&uuml;rdig zu machen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Dabei sind meine Bedenken und &Auml;ngste in den &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Staaten selbst l&auml;ngst best&auml;tigt. Warum h&ouml;rt man nicht auf Leopold Kohr (Das Ende der Gro&szlig;en), Ernst Friedrich Schumacher (Small is beautiful), Jimmy Goldsmith (Le pi&egrave;ge - et si nous avions suivi la mauvaise route?), Henry Coston (L&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;europe des banquiers), Jean Pierre Chevenement, Margaret Thatcher, Philippe Seguin, Marie-France Garaud, Elisabeth Guigou, Alberto Miele (Cacciamo i mercanti dal tempio dell&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;europa), Gerard de Selys, Dr. Manfred Brunner (Anti-Maastricht-Partei), Sir Ralf Dahrendorf (Ex-EU-Kommissar: &quot;k&uuml;nstliche Superkonstruktion nicht lebensf&auml;hig&quot;), Denis de Rougemont (L&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&#039;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;europe doit se faire pour la diversit&eacute;) und unz&auml;hlige andere Warner.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&Ouml;sterreich ist von der Geschichte auserw&auml;hlt, Beispiel und Zentrum und Halt in Mitteleuropa zu sein. &Ouml;sterreich ist eine Br&uuml;cke der Hoffnung zum Osten.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wir haben seit dem Krieg in m&uuml;hevoller Arbeit ein riesiges Kapital an Wohlstand, innerem Frieden, internationalem Respekt und Glaubw&uuml;rdigkeit aufgebaut als unabh&auml;ngige, liebenswerte, friedliebende Kulturnation im Herzen Europas. Das kann nicht kurzsichtig und verantwortungslos aufs Spiel gesetzt werden.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Gerade jetzt nach dem Zerfall der kommunistischen Diktatur und der &Ouml;ffnung der Grenzen muss sich &Ouml;sterreich seiner Verantwortung in Europa bewusst werden und darf sich nicht selbst eliminieren.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Mit einer uns suggerierten Torschlusspanik wird eine Anschlussneurose erzeugt. Angst vor was oder wem? Welche Feinde hat &Ouml;sterreich? Wer sollte und warum &Ouml;sterreichs Sicherheit gef&auml;hrden? Gerade durch den Anschluss an einen Milit&auml;rblock w&uuml;rde &Ouml;sterreich als &quot;Randgebiet Ostmark&quot; erst zum Aufmarschgebiet und zum Feindbild und Angriffsziel werden (Warnung von Erwin Lanc). Gegen atomare Bedrohung ist kein Kraut gewachsen und bei Regionalkriegen - siehe Bosnien - gibt es keinen &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Schutz, nicht einmal in Nordirland, innerhalb der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; selbst.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&Ouml;sterreichs Neutralit&auml;t ist gerade jetzt n&ouml;tiger als je zuvor. Man muss die Neutralit&auml;t beim Namen nennen und zu ihr stehen. Neutralit&auml;t ist ein wahrer Wert. Die immerw&auml;hrende Neutralit&auml;t ist das Fundament unseres Staates und darf nicht verraten und ausgeh&ouml;hlt werden. Wenn wir dieses Fundament unterminieren, zerst&ouml;ren wir diesen unseren Staat &Ouml;sterreich, der darauf errichtet ist.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ab jetzt bedeutet die Neutralit&auml;t &Ouml;sterreichs Selbst&auml;ndigkeit, Unabh&auml;ngigkeit, Freiheit, Verantwortung tragen, Beispiel geben, eine aktive Neutralit&auml;t. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Auch hier ist die Schweiz ein Beispiel und wird auch im Staatsvertrag als Beispiel genannt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es besteht kein Anlass, gerade jetzt einen Graben quer durch Europa zu ziehen. Es ist so als ob &ouml;stlich von Wien Feindesland w&auml;re.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; Die Grenzposten werden von Deutschland an den eben beseitigten Eisernen Vorhang verlegt!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&nbsp; Diese neue Grenzziehung ist nicht nur quer durch Europa, sondern quer durch &Ouml;sterreich, wo die Donaumonarchie war. Es w&auml;re verantwortungslos und gef&auml;hrlich, durch den Anschluss an eine wirtschaftliche und politische &Uuml;bermacht das Gef&auml;lle zu und die Bedrohung f&uuml;r die L&auml;nder &quot;drau&szlig;en&quot; zu vergr&ouml;&szlig;ern. &Ouml;sterreichs kulturelle, wirtschaftliche und geschichtliche Bestimmung, &Ouml;sterreichs Verantwortung und Ausstrahlung liegt im Osten. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;(Das besagt auch der Name &Ouml;sterreich.)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Fronten haben sich gewandelt. Es sind nicht mehr die politischen Grenzen, sondern die Front verl&auml;uft zwischen der brutalen, nur wirtschaftsinteressierten Wegwerfgesellschaft und der ausgebeuteten Natur und der zerst&ouml;rten Seele des Menschen. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es gibt einen neuen Widerstand und schon wieder feige Kollaborateure.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die jetzt verantwortlichen Politiker sind Hampelm&auml;nner der Wirtschaftsinteressen und heucheln Umweltbewusstsein und Kulturbewusstsein mit Lippenbekenntnissen. Sie beschlie&szlig;en umweltzerst&ouml;rende und kulturzerst&ouml;rende Ma&szlig;nahmen, die unsere Zukunft in Frage stellen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die sogenannte &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; betreibt die brutale Vernichtung unserer Lebensbasis, unserer uralten Kulturen, unserer kleinen, gewachsenen Eigenst&auml;ndigkeiten, unseres Artenreichtums und unserer Selbstachtung.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; ist eine riesige Handelsvertretung des Gro&szlig;unternehmertums, der Gewerkschaften, Genossenschaften, der Gro&szlig;banken, der Giftkonzerne, der Monokultur-Monopolisten und der Atom-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; und Gen-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;L&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;obby, die uns wie brave Schafe gemeinsam wie das Schlachtvieh in einen Zug in die falsche Richtung verladen will.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Dieser riesigen Wirtschaftsmafia geht es nur um Macht und Geld und nicht um das Wohl der Natur und des Menschen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Eine von verantwortungslosen Schreibtischstrategen ferngesteuerte gigantische Fehlplanung zerst&ouml;rt die Fundamente unseres &uuml;ber uralte Zeiten gewachsenen Europas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Europa erlebt die gr&ouml;&szlig;te Vergewaltigung seiner Geschichte.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Aus Br&uuml;ssel kommt keine geistige und kulturelle Erneuerung Europas. Von dort kommen keine Antworten auf die Fragen, die das Gewissen der V&ouml;lker Europas beunruhigen (Alberto Miele). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Aus dieser neuen Hegemonie kommen keine Botschaften, die die Identit&auml;t, unsere uralten Werte, die Inhalte unserer Zivilisation und die Sehns&uuml;chte der Menschen Europas betreffen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wo sind die Kulturen, die Religionen, die Philosophien, die ein neues europ&auml;isches Zeitalter aus der Taufe heben?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Gerade jetzt, wo unsere Gesellschaft die Grenzen des Wachstums erreicht, ist Dezentralisierung unsere einzige &Uuml;berlebenschance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ein Anschluss an diese &uuml;berm&auml;chtige Zentralgewalt, die noch immer Wirtschaftswachstum als Zentraldogma gegen alle Evidenz durchziehen will, hat f&uuml;r alle Beteiligten katastrophale Folgen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wohin diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; uns mithineinziehen will, ist ein gnadenloser Konkurrenzkampf, ein Amoklauf in eine gro&szlig;e, gef&auml;hrliche Illusion, in die Sackgasse des Wirtschaftswachstums. Es w&auml;re Wahnsinn, diesem exklusiven Klub der Wegwerfgesellschaft beizutreten, der sich selbst in den M&uuml;ll wirft und ad absurdum f&uuml;hrt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wenn das Produkt &quot;EU&quot; so gut ist, warum muss man derart intensiv daf&uuml;r werben? Und dieser verd&auml;chtige Zeitdruck: Wir m&uuml;ssen uns sofort enteignen, sonst ist es zu sp&auml;t! &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Alle guten Dinge geschehen langsam in einem organischen Ablauf von selbst. Einen Baum kann man auch nicht mit Drohungen &uuml;berzeugen und &uuml;berreden, da&szlig; er im tiefen Winter zu bl&uuml;hen hat.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ich verstehe nicht, warum man uns mit Gewalt &uuml;berreden will, die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;, dieses sinkende Schiff zu besteigen, und zwar sofort.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; ist eine riesige Titanic. Die Analogien zum Untergang der Titanic sind erschreckend. Hier wie dort: Konzeptlosigkeit, Gr&ouml;&szlig;enwahn, Ma&szlig;losigkeit, blinde Technologiegl&auml;ubigkeit und Geschwindigkeitswahn um jeden Preis. Dort das Rennen um das &quot;blaue Band&quot; in die t&ouml;dlichen Eisberge, hier das m&ouml;rderische Wettrennen an die Grenzen des Wachstums der Wegwerfgesellschaft, die unsere Umwelt und uns selbst zerst&ouml;rt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;So einen &quot;europ&auml;ischen Ungl&uuml;cksdampfer&quot; besteigt man nicht und vertraut man unser Leben und unsere Zukunft nicht an. Da ist es besser, man bleibt in einem kleinen, aber man&ouml;vrierbaren Boot.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;In praktisch der ganzen &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; geht es wild zu: Nordirland, Baskenland, Korsika, Mafia, Comorra, Ausl&auml;nderverfolgungen, Rassenhass und Pogrome, Diskriminierung von Gr&ouml;nl&auml;ndern, Macedoniern und Bretonen, brutale Streiks, blutige Ausschreitungen, Studentenrevolten, Drogenkriminalit&auml;t, nukleare St&ouml;rf&auml;lle, verw&uuml;stete Landstriche, Apathie und Katastrophenstimmung, Jugendkriminalit&auml;t, bald 20 Millionen Arbeitslose und eine Staatsspaltung in Flamen und Wallonen, ausgerechnet in Br&uuml;ssel, dem Sitz der &quot;Europ&auml;ischen Union&quot;. Im Vergleich dazu haben das &quot;isolierte &Ouml;sterreich&quot; und die skandinavischen L&auml;nder, die man unbedingt in die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; treiben will, es &quot;drau&szlig;en&quot; noch gut.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es wird in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; mit Menschenschicksalen jongliert als w&auml;ren es Bauern auf dem Schachbrett. Man kann doch freie Bauern nicht mit Geld abspeisen und ins Ausgedinge schicken, das ist erniedrigend, oder sie nur noch als Folklore- und Alibibauern ben&uuml;tzen, zum Herzeigen f&uuml;r den Tourismus. Das geht gegen Ehre und Selbstachtung, das ist &auml;rger als Mord.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Man bezahlt die Bauern f&uuml;r ihren Selbstmord. Die EU verlangt von den Bauern, sie sollen ihre eigene uralte Kultur zerst&ouml;ren. Daf&uuml;r bekommen sie Geld. Anders als bei der Katastrophenhilfe wird die Katastrophe erst mutwillig in Gang gesetzt. Umgebrachte gewachsene Strukturen kann man auch mit sehr viel Geld nicht wiedergutmachen. Tote kann man mit Geld nicht zum Leben erwecken.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Der Wunsch einiger m&auml;chtiger und konkurrenzf&auml;higer Gro&szlig;industrieller nach Eintritt in die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; ist, noch mehr wirtschaftliche Vorteile zu erlangen. Das geht jedoch auf Kosten der sowieso schon gef&auml;hrdeten Kleinbetriebe und Kleinbauern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ich wei&szlig; aus eigener Erfahrung, dass in den &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Staaten z.B. in Frankreich nur Agrargenossenschaften &uuml;ber 100 ha eine &Uuml;berlebenschance haben.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Das schaut dann so aus: entweder brachliegende, ver&ouml;dete Felder, verlassene D&ouml;rfer oder Nivellierung von Terrain, Beseitigung von f&uuml;r Gro&szlig;maschinen st&ouml;rende W&auml;ldchen, B&auml;umen und Felsen, Nivellierung von uralten Geh&ouml;ften, Begradigung von B&auml;chen. Eine perfide Zerst&ouml;rung, die in ihren gigantischen Auswirkungen jeden Krieg &uuml;bersteigt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Vermehrte Verwendung von Kunstd&uuml;nger, Pestiziden, genetischen Manipulationen, Bestrahlungen und Umweltgiften aller Art, nat&uuml;rlich in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; erzeugt. Eine sadistische, technokratische Zerst&ouml;rung jeglicher Romantik mit dem Schlagwort: unrentabel. Monokultur, so weit das Auge reicht. Dem Bauern wird befohlen, unsere &Uuml;berlebensgrundlage systematisch zu vergewaltigen, den ihm zu treuen H&auml;nden anvertrauten Grund und Boden, Wald und Fluren zu vergiften und zu zerst&ouml;ren. Die Landwirtschaft wird zur gigantischen Agro-Business-Industrie.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Abh&auml;ngigkeit der Bauern und von uns allen von Industrie, Chemie und Monopolwirtschaft, diese neue Leibeigenschaft, wird durch einen Anschluss an die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; ins Unertr&auml;gliche gesteigert.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ausl&auml;ndische, m&auml;chtigere, brutalere Befehlshaber treten an die Stelle der einheimischen kleineren Firmen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ebenso ergeht es den Kleineren, d. h. allen menschlichen Betrieben, sie werden vernichtet, daf&uuml;r gibt es noch mehr Gro&szlig;kaufh&auml;user, Gro&szlig;banken und Gro&szlig;industrialisierung. Kurzum alles, was unser aller Leben romantisch, liebens- und lebenswert macht, hat kaum mehr &Uuml;berlebensm&ouml;glichkeit. Die stupiden Brutalit&auml;ten siegen, die delikaten Werte kommen um, weil sie sich nicht wehren k&ouml;nnen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Agro-Business-Industrie in der EU betreibt fast analog dem &bdquo;Dritten Reich&quot; eine brutale Auslese von reinrassigen gleichgeschalteten &quot;Elite&quot;-Produkten und eine Eliminierung von &quot;minderwertigem&quot; Erbgut oder Saatgut.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es beginnt mit den sch&ouml;nen gro&szlig;en &Auml;pfeln, die alle gleich sein m&uuml;ssen, die in Monokultur gez&uuml;chtet sind, in gleicher Rasse, mit gleichem Geschmack, und setzt sich fort in der genetischen &quot;Nutztierveredelung&quot; und den Legehennenbatterien. Alles nicht produktive Leben wird eliminiert. Alle nicht profitable Vielfalt, alle Andersartigkeit, alle Kleinteiligkeit, aller nutzloser Artenreichtum, alle unrentable Sch&ouml;nheit wird vernichtet. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Dadurch sterben auch das Kleinbauerntum, die Familienbetriebe, die Romantik, kurzum unsere Lebensqualit&auml;t.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Durch das Sterben der Grei&szlig;ler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; (Gemischtwarenhandlungen),&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; der Bauern, der Familien- und Kleinbetriebe, durch das Sterben der kleinen Identit&auml;ten entsteht eine Gleichschaltung und eine Anonymisierung unserer Gesellschaft. Man raubt dem Menschen seine W&uuml;rde. Dies bringt eine neue Abh&auml;ngigkeit, eine neue Versklavung, eine neue Leibeigenschaft noch nie dagewesenen Ausma&szlig;es hervor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Das ist das Ende des humanistischen Europas. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Was dann &uuml;brigbleibt ist keine menschengerechte, sondern eine maschinengerechte und computergerechte Welt. Es ist eine Zerst&ouml;rung von h&ouml;heren Werten, die in ihrer Vielfalt Europa ausmachen. Es ist die Zerst&ouml;rung Europas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Kleinbauern m&uuml;ssen Haus und Hof und Land verkaufen, werden entweder arbeitslos oder Stadtproletariat oder m&uuml;ssen sich Agro-Business-Genossenschaften anschlie&szlig;en, wo sie nur mehr Befehlsempf&auml;nger ohne Entscheidungsfreiheit sind, auf einem Land, das einmal ihnen geh&ouml;rte.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; leidet unter einem wachsenden Arbeitslosenheer, das schon jetzt der arbeitenden Bev&ouml;lkerung eines Landes 7- bis 10-mal so gro&szlig; wie &Ouml;sterreich entspricht!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Man kann sich vorstellen, welches verheerende Beispiel die &lt;strong&gt;EU &lt;/strong&gt;damit der Welt gibt, wenn die 3 Milliarden Menschen, die in der Dritten Welt auf dem Lande ihr Auskommen finden, diesem &lt;strong&gt;EU B&lt;/strong&gt;eispiel zu folgen gezwungen werden. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Eine gigantische Fl&uuml;chtlingswelle von 2 Milliarden Landbev&ouml;lkerung - diesen &quot;exode rural mondial&quot;, wie Jimmy Goldsmith warnt, k&ouml;nne die Welt nicht mehr ertragen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Grenzen sind so wie unsere Haut. Sie sch&uuml;tzen den gewachsenen Organismus, unsere individuelle Andersartigkeit vor Gefahr von Au&szlig;en wie Hitze und K&auml;lte. Wenn man die Haut entfernt, stirbt der Organismus, weil er schutzlos wird.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; Daher haben wir Schutzz&ouml;lle zum Schutz einer gef&auml;hrdeten Gemeinschaft. &auml;hnlich wie wir Sonnenbrillen und Zeckenimpfungen etc. zu unserem Schutz einsetzen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Was Gott getrennt hat, sollen wir nicht mit Gewalt einen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es gibt nat&uuml;rliche Grenzen wie zum Beispiel die Sahara, das Mittelmeer und die Alpen, in deren Schutz sich uralte Kulturen gebildet haben wie die afrikanischen, die mediterranen und die nordeurop&auml;ischen Kulturen. Die Alpen haben eine Schutzfunktion sowohl f&uuml;r den Norden als auch f&uuml;r den S&uuml;den.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ein schrankenloser, sinnloser Transitverkehr ist gleichbedeutend mit einem Niederrei&szlig;en und Nivellieren der Alpen, auch wenn der Verkehr untertunnelt wird. &Ouml;sterreich hat genauso wie die Schweiz eine Alpine Schutzw&auml;chterfunktion f&uuml;r Europa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die fieberhafte, unnat&uuml;rliche, konzeptlose Hin- und Herraserei ist Wahnsinn und wird in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; zum &quot;grenzenlosen Wahnsinn&quot;. An dem Ort, wo wir sind, machen wir alles hin, dann fl&uuml;chten wir vor unserer eigenen Zerst&ouml;rung, um anderswo alles hin zu machen, und auf dem Weg dahin wird auch alles hin. Dieser falsche Trend wird in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; forciert und unterst&uuml;tzt. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Elisabeth Guigou dr&uuml;ckt das so aus: Eine Wirtschaft, die nur auf Kurzzeit-Rentabilit&auml;t ausgerichtet ist, ohne Plan, ohne Vision, ohne Sinn, die arbeitsstellen-fressende Maschinen produziert, die mehr und mehr von der Transport- und Kommunikationsgeschwindigkeit abh&auml;ngig ist und die unter Au&szlig;erachtlassung des &ouml;kologischen Gleichgewichtes die Menschen zu einer ebenso forcierten Beweglichkeit zwingt wie die Waren, die Kapitalien, die Technologien und Informationen unter Missachtung der Menschenw&uuml;rde und des Schutzes der gewohnten Lebensweisen, eine &ouml;konomische Diktatur, die &uuml;ber alle anderen menschlichen T&auml;tigkeiten triumphiert...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wenn man das, was man zu sch&uuml;tzen hat, vorher umbringt, braucht man keinen Schutz mehr. Zuerst m&uuml;ssen die Bauern und die Grei&szlig;ler&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; (Gemischtwarenhandlungen)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; weg und die Kleinbetriebe und der &quot;nutzlose&quot; Artenreichtum, die &quot;unrentable&quot; Vielfalt. Zuerst m&uuml;ssen wir uns angleichen an internationales Mittelma&szlig;, an vergiftetes Essen, genmanipulierte und bestrahlte Lebensmittel. Zuerst m&uuml;ssen wir in vorauseilendem Gehorsam uns selbst nivellieren und uns vernichten, dann kann die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; widerstandslos einmarschieren und durchmarschieren.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&Ouml;sterreich als ganzes wird ein Vasallenstaat, eine neue Ostmark. Selbstverst&auml;ndlich ist dann &Ouml;sterreichs Position als neutrale, kernkraftfreie, umweltbewusste Nation kaum mehr haltbar. &Ouml;sterreich kann dann nicht mehr selbst entscheiden, was es tut, was und wieviel es produziert und in welche L&auml;nder es exportiert und aus welchen es importiert. &Ouml;sterreichs Geschicke werden von fremden Leuten in Br&uuml;ssel oder anderswo in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; bestimmt, von Schreibtischstrategen, die sich einen Dreck um &Ouml;sterreichs Eigenst&auml;ndigkeit scheren.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&Uuml;ber &Ouml;sterreichs Neutralit&auml;tswillen, &uuml;ber &Ouml;sterreichs Umweltbewusstsein wird in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Kommandozentrale nur gelacht.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Der Slogan &quot;einsam oder gemeinsam&quot; ist eine angstmachende, demagogische Aufforderung zur Verunsicherung, zur Unfreiheit und zur Abh&auml;ngigkeit. Es mag paradox klingen, aber allein ist jeder am st&auml;rksten. Aus pers&ouml;nlicher Erfahrung wei&szlig; ich, dass ein Aussenstehender genauso stark ist wie die Gruppe und nicht schw&auml;cher. Der Au&szlig;enstehende ist beweglicher, effektiver in seinem Handeln und im Reagieren als eine schwerf&auml;llige, b&uuml;rokratische, chaotische Organisation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Europa ist nur stark dank der Vielfalt seiner Eigenst&auml;ndigkeiten. Diese kleinteilige Vielfalt muss verst&auml;rkt und gesch&uuml;tzt werden. Diese Vielfalt ist Europa. Schon de Gaulle erkannte, dass Europa nur eine Chance als Europa der selbst&auml;ndigen, freien Vaterl&auml;nder hat. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es ist unverst&auml;ndlich, wie verantwortungslos unsere Politiker jetzt unser wertvollstes Gut, unsere Unabh&auml;ngigkeit, Freiheit und Eigenst&auml;ndigkeit aufgeben und &Ouml;sterreich entm&uuml;ndigen wollen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es ist ein Verrat an &Ouml;sterreich. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Beim letzten Anschluss gab es auch jede Menge Seyss-Inquarts, Guislings, Petains, die in der damaligen Situation wahrscheinlich auch aus &Uuml;berzeugung und Patriotismus glaubten, das Richtige zu tun und ihre Pflicht erf&uuml;llen zu m&uuml;ssen, indem sie ihr Land einer fremden Hegemonie anvertrauten. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Heute lehrt uns die Geschichte, dass ihr Tun falsch und sch&auml;dlich war, und sie sind l&auml;ngst als Verr&auml;ter und Kollaborateure gebrandmarkt, bestraft und hingerichtet worden. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Mitgefangen - mitgehangen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Unter der Dunstglocke der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; wird von allen unbemerkt der Anschluss an Deutschland vollzogen. Wenn dann diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; Schiffbruch erleidet, haben wir noch ein St&uuml;ck mehr unserer Unabh&auml;ngigkeit verloren und bleiben am gro&szlig;en deutschen Bruder kleben.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Bei Wahrung aller Unterschiede hat &Ouml;sterreich &Auml;hnliches bereits erlebt, als auch aus wirtschaftlichen Gr&uuml;nden 1937-1938 ein Anschluss an das &quot;Altreich&quot; propagiert wurde. &quot;Heim ins Reich&quot; hie&szlig; damals die Parole. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Beim Umtausch des Schilling in den Gro&szlig;macht-Euro muss man fatalerweise Analogien mit dem Umtausch des Schilling 1938 in die Reichsmark feststellen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Man darf nicht vergessen, dass das Versprechen einer finanziellen und wirtschaftlichen Besserstellung der k&uuml;nftigen Ostm&auml;rker Haupttriebfeder vieler &Ouml;sterreicher war, um f&uuml;r den Anschluss zu stimmen. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Auf die bejubelte Einverleibung mit Gro&szlig;deutschland erfolgte die Ern&uuml;chterung. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Jetzt ist es &auml;hnlich. Genau das, was man uns in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; vorgaukeln will, verlieren wir in der&lt;strong&gt; EU&lt;/strong&gt;: sozialen Wohlstand, Vollbesch&auml;ftigung, eine intakte Umwelt, unsere hohe Lebensqualit&auml;t, unsere Heimat, unsere Selbstachtung, unsere Natur und unsere uralten Kulturen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Europ&auml;er ist man nur dann, wenn man sein unabh&auml;ngiges, eigenst&auml;ndiges Europ&auml;ertum bewahrt und hochh&auml;lt. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Schweiz, wohlhabend und demokratisch, auch im Herzen Europas gelegen, soll uns ein leuchtendes Beispiel sein.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ich verstehe auch nicht, wieso unser Bundespr&auml;sident uns zur Aufgabe unserer Souver&auml;nit&auml;t auffordert. Er m&uuml;sste doch als oberster Patriot warnen und die Verfassung sch&uuml;tzen. Ist denn Landesverrat kein Vergehen, wenn man &Ouml;sterreich einer ausl&auml;ndischen Zentralgewalt unterwerfen will? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Der Staatsvertrag brachte &Ouml;sterreich die Befreiung. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; Vertrag ist eine Kapitulation &Ouml;sterreichs, eine Entm&uuml;ndigung &Ouml;sterreichs, eine Unterwerfung unter eine neue anachronistische Hegemonie - und ein Bruch des Staatsvertrages.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es ist unglaublich: Die Politiker bereiten den zweiten Anschluss vor und wollen das &ouml;sterreichische Volk vor vollendete Tatsachen stellen. Sind unsere Politiker von allen guten Geistern verlassen, so dass erst&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; die Geschichte&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; sie zurechtweisen muss? &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Ich bin kein Jurist, aber ich bin der festen &Uuml;berzeugung, dass wir von m&auml;chtigen Interessensgruppen au&szlig;erhalb jeder ethischen, geschichtlichen, moralischen, kulturellen und &ouml;kologischen Legalit&auml;t mit einer miesen Demagogie manipuliert werden, so wie seinerzeit bei Zwentendorf&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; (Inbetriebnahme des Atommeilers wurde durch Volksabstimmung verhindert)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Staaten werden nivelliert und anonymisiert und ihrer Identit&auml;t beraubt. In diese Richtung geht es und nicht in die Richtung der Dezentralisation und&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; Vertiefung&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; der Eigenst&auml;ndigkeiten. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Zum Beweis gen&uuml;gt die &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Fahne mit den jetzt 12 genau gleichen 5-zackigen Sternchen. Welches dieser Sternchen w&uuml;rde &Ouml;sterreich symbolisieren, etwa das dritte rechts von unten oder das zweite, das genauso aussieht?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Der F&uuml;nfstern ist kein Symbol aus der europ&auml;ischen und schon gar nicht aus der &ouml;sterreichischen Geschichte. Er kommt in der Entwicklung der Staaten des Okzidents nicht vor. Das Pentagramm, ein okkultistisches Zeichen der Druden und Freimaurer ist ein Fremdk&ouml;rper in der abendl&auml;ndischen Heraldik. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die 5-zackigen Sterne dienen eher als Merkmal der Unterwerfung, Inbesitznahme und Kolonisierung wie auf der austral-neuseel&auml;ndischen, amerikanischen und auf Kolonialfahnen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Fahne ist noch dazu ein Plagiat aus dem Sternenbanner. Auch die Vereinigten Staaten Amerikas waren als 5-zackige Sternchen, wei&szlig; auf blau, zuerst im Kreis angeordnet, genauso wie jetzt die M&ouml;chtegern-&quot;Vereinigten Staaten Europas&quot;. Sp&auml;ter, als sie sich vermehrten, wurden sie in Reih und Glied gebracht. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Diese 5-zackigen Sternchen sind dieselben wie der Sowjetstern, der Stern der jugoslawischen, chinesischen, kubanischen und sonstigen Volksrepubliken. Wahrlich, dieses Symbol ist ein Armutszeugnis f&uuml;r die gewachsenen Identit&auml;ten Europas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es ist ein b&ouml;ses Omen, wenn schon das Zeichen falsch ist. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Diese &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Sternchenfahne symbolisiert die Selbstaufgabe Europas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;In der sogenannten &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; ist die Kultur weniger als Nebensache. Die sch&ouml;pferischen Kr&auml;fte werden zu n&uuml;tzlichen Idioten getrimmt. Zur Unterst&uuml;tzung und Verbr&auml;mung und Legitimierung eines merkantilen und industriellen Wachstums, das sich selbst zerst&ouml;rt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Die Kultur ist in Br&uuml;ssel nicht pr&auml;sent. Sie ist in der nur merkantilen und industriellen &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; kein Thema. In Br&uuml;ssel kennt man den Preis von allem und den Wert von nichts. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Es geht in dieser kulturlosen, sogenannten &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; nur um Zahlen: Produktionszahlen, Termine und Laufzeiten, &Uuml;bergangsfristen, Einwohner- und Viehzahlen. Bruttosozialprodukte, Anbau-, Wald- und Weidegebiete in Quadratkilometern, Lohnkosten, Sozialleistungen, Nebenkosten. Exportziffern, Tonnenzahlen f&uuml;r Schwertransporte, Milchpreise, Preisanpassungen, Finanzierungszahlen, Ausgleichszahlen, Prozente, Preissenkungen, Zucker-, Milch&shy;- und Fischquoten, Transitbeschr&auml;nkungen in Zahlen, Kontingente, Mitfinanzierungen, Tabellen, Statistiken, Marktzugangsbeschr&auml;nkungen in Zahlen. Laufzeiten, Ecu Umtauschkurse, hohe Arbeitslosenzahlen, niedrige Besch&auml;ftigungszahlen, F&ouml;rderungs- und Subventionszahlen, die Anzahl von &Ouml;kopunkten, Geldzahlungen aller Art, irreale Wirtschaftswachstumszahlen, Umfrageergebnisse in Zahlen und Prozenten, Stimmenanzahlen des Ministerrates und der Sperrminorit&auml;t, Mehrheiten, Minderheiten, Abstimmungsergebnisse, EU-Werbeausgaben. Ja sogar H&ouml;henzahlen f&uuml;r Bergbauern in Metern und Breitegradzahlen f&uuml;r die Landwirtschaft in Finnland. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Wenn das nicht symptomatisch ist. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Auch der Umweltschutz ist in der Br&uuml;sseler Hegemonie abwesend. Nur 0,3 Prozent (30 von 10.000) der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt;-Beamten sind f&uuml;r die &Ouml;kologie t&auml;tig. Vom Grenzen &uuml;berbr&uuml;ckenden Umweltschutz ist nur die Rede. &Ouml;sterreich muss die Kernkraft mitfinanzieren und z. B. Plastikflaschen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; und Gen-Produkte&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; und idiotisch-gef&auml;hrliche Richtlinien f&uuml;r Apfelgr&ouml;&szlig;en und Monokultur-Obstsorten &uuml;bernehmen. Das habe ich selbst gesehen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Von Kultur und den Werten des Abendlandes ist in Br&uuml;ssel keine Rede. Um Ausgaben f&uuml;r Kultur muss man erst Br&uuml;ssel bitten. Das Kulturstudium und auch der gesamte Studienbereich in der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; wird ausgerichtet auf die N&uuml;tzlichkeit f&uuml;r die Industrie und auf das forcierte Wachstum.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Nur die Sch&ouml;pfung kann uns Kreativit&auml;t und organisches Wachstum lehren. Nur die Sch&ouml;pfung kann uns Achtung lehren vor dem Artenreichtum und der unglaublichen Vielfalt, deren Teil wir selbst sind.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;In der &lt;strong&gt;EU&lt;/strong&gt; aber gehen die Bestrebungen in die genau umgekehrte Richtung: Vernichtung der kleinteiligen sch&ouml;pferischen Werte zugunsten einer v&ouml;llig falschen und &uuml;berholten Automatisierung, Zentralisierung und Rationalisierung, die uns &uuml;ber kurz oder lang zum Untergang bringt.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Das Gewissen unserer Zivilisation, unsere uralte Bestimmung, h&ouml;here Werte anzustreben, bleibt auf der Strecke.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_occasion_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Written in Vienna &ndash; Paris &ndash; Kaurinui, 1988&ndash;1994. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Passages in italics: La Picaudi&egrave;re, 1997.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_occasion_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;Geschrieben in Wien - Paris - Kaurinui, 1988 - 1994,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%&quot;&gt; erg&auml;nzt in kursiv in La Picaudi&egrave;re, 1997.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
text_published_en-'&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Witzany, G&uuml;nther (ed.): Verraten und Verkauft - Das EG-Lesebuch. UNIPRESS: Salzburg, 1993, p. 65-68 (Text Anschlu&szlig;psychose, 1988) (German)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;protokolle&lt;/em&gt;. Zeitschrift f&uuml;r Literatur und Kunst. edited by Otto Breicha. Verlagsb&uuml;ro Lehner: Vienna, 1997, pp. 185-193 (German)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Witzany, G&uuml;nther (ed.): Zukunft &Ouml;sterreich - EU Anschlu&szlig; und die Folgen. UNIPRESS: Salzburg, 1998, p. 83-99 (German)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Schmied, Wieland (ed.): Hundertwasser 1928&ndash;2000, Catalogue Raisonn&eacute;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Vol. II: F&uuml;rst, Andrea Christa: Catalogue Raisonn&eacute;. Taschen: Cologne, 2002, pp. 1151-1162 (German and English)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. (Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Langen M&uuml;ller: Munich, 2004, pp. 55-64 (German)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;',
text_published_ge-'&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Witzany, G&uuml;nther (Hg.): Verraten und Verkauft - Das EG-Lesebuch. UNIPRESS: Salzburg 1993, S. 65-68 (Text &lt;span style=&quot;background: yellow 0% 50%; moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial&quot;&gt;Anschlu&szlig;psychose&lt;/span&gt;, 1988)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;protokolle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;. Zeitschrift f&uuml;r Literatur und Kunst. hrsg. von Otto Breicha. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Verlagsb&uuml;ro Lehner: Wien 1997, S. 185-193&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Witzany, G&uuml;nther (Hg.): Zukunft &Ouml;sterreich - EU Anschlu&szlig; und die Folgen. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;UNIPRESS: Salzburg 1998, S. 83-99&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schmied, Wieland (Hg.): Hundertwasser 1928&ndash;2000, Catalogue Raisonn&eacute; / Werkverzeichnis. Vol. II: F&uuml;r&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;st, Andrea Christa: Catalogue Raisonn&eacute; / Werkverzeichnis. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 2002, S. 1151-1162 (Deutsch und Englisch)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Langen M&uuml;ller: M&uuml;nchen 2004, S. 55-64&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 150%&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;',
