%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.4.5.2
object(text,'1.4.5.2','Hundertwasser’s campaign against Austria’s joining of the European Union 1988-1994',[
id-131,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-131,
txt-'1.4.5.2',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'Hundertwasser&rsquo;s campaign against Austria&rsquo;s joining of the European Union 1988-1994',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'2006-00-00',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As early as 1988, Hundertwasser noted in an essay that integration in the E. U. was not a good solution for Austria, and that Austria would lose its independence, its autonomy, its neutrality and its credibility as a peace-loving culture nation at the heart of Europe if the country were to join the E. U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;During 1993 and 1994 Hundertwasser repeatedly and emphatically spoke out against Austria&rsquo;s joining of the European Union. He expressed his reservations in the manifesto &lt;em&gt;To Join the E. U. Is to Betray &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Austria&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; and Betray &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Europe&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;',
text_contents_en-'&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;As early as 1988, Hundertwasser noted in an essay that integration in the E. U. was not a good solution for Austria, and that Austria would lose its independence, its autonomy, its neutrality and its credibility as a peace-loving culture nation at the heart of Europe if the country were to join the E. U.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;During 1993 and 1994 Hundertwasser repeatedly and emphatically spoke out against Austria&rsquo;s joining of the European Union. He expressed his reservations in the manifesto &lt;em&gt;To Join the E. U. Is to Betray &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Austria&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt; and Betray &lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;Europe&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br /&gt;',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Schon in seinem Text von 1988 &bdquo;Anschlu&szlig;psychose&ldquo; formulierte Hundertwasser seine &Uuml;berzeugung, da&szlig; ein Anschlu&szlig; an die EG (Europ&auml;ische Gemeinschaft) keine gute Sache f&uuml;r &Ouml;sterreich w&auml;re und da&szlig; &Ouml;sterreich im Falle eines Beitritts zur EG seine Eigenst&auml;ndigkeit, seine Unabh&auml;ngigkeit, seine Neutralit&auml;t und seine Glaubw&uuml;rdigkeit als friedliebende Kulturnation im Herzen Europas verlieren w&uuml;rde. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;In den Jahren 1993 und 1994 trat Hundertwasser immer wieder vehement gegen einen Beitritt &Ouml;sterreichs zur Europ&auml;ischen Union ein und formulierte seine Bedenken in dem Manifest &lt;em&gt;EU Beitritt ist Verrat an &Ouml;sterreich und Verrat an Europa.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'',
text_occasion_ge-'',
text_published_en-'',
text_published_ge-'',
text_author-'Hundertwasser Archiv',
text_orig_lang-'',
text_translator-'',
text_source_en-'',
