%Andrea###2009-06-26 07:25:11###object###text###1.5.1.5
object(text,'1.5.1.5','HUNDERTWASSERS ’S LETTER TO MINICH',[
id-136,
typeOfObject-'TEXT',
text_id-136,
txt-'1.5.1.5',
text_type-'',
text_category-'',
text_title_en-'HUNDERTWASSERS &rsquo;S LETTER TO MINICH',
text_title_ge-'',
text_keywords-'',
text_date-'1988-06-03',
text_summary_en-'',
text_summary_ge-'',
text_language-'en',
text_contents-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;My dear friend Minich,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thank you for your letter of 25 May, RE the Spittelau district heating station.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I fully understand that you are against it, just like myself and many other concerned people. I personally grew up in the Brigittenau area, in other words very close by.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But your letter lacks a practical alternative for today.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We ourselves, all of us, every Viennese citizen, are responsible for our own refuse. If we produced no refuse, there would be none to burn. Let us boycott waste-incineration plants by simply not supplying them with refuse. Is that feasible in present-day &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;? Refuse should be made a criminal offence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Refuse producers, packaging industries, refuse causers, refuse makers, i.e. all of us, should be severely punished in order to induce a radical avoidance of waste.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I spent a year agonizing over the same arguments for declining the project as yours, before finally deciding to accept the commission for the visual redesign of the plant. As you know, I am vehemently against all environmental pollutants and have always used all my means to promote a waste-free society.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I am a realist, however.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We cannot close our eyes to reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;All my utopias and dreams can be realized, as I am continually demonstrating.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Having made a detailed study of what would happen if Spittelau did not go into operation, i.e. by thinking it through to the end, I decided the negative consequences are far worse.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We won&rsquo;t have a waste-free society tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But hopefully the day after tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I will fight vehemently for it, and we must all work daily towards it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The negative points:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Refuse incineration in a built-up urban area with the fear that toxins will endanger people in the city.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Skipping the humus phase by incinerating.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The positive points:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Extensive, almost complete neutralization of toxic substances in refuse through incineration in new (state-of-the-art) denox filter plants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Heat extraction: It will heat 10-15 % of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;3.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Following my redesign the works will lose their ugliness, and thus the psychological distress caused by the earlier sight of its immense and visibly threatening pollution of the environment will be relieved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I am certain that people will even feel pride at having this new symbol of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; in their neighbourhood, and this will increase the self-confidence and joy in life of an entire city district. Particularly when the filter plant and technical section are setting examples to the world. However paradoxical it sounds, I see the Spittelau station as a first call for a more attractive, waste-free environment. I am also proud that &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Austria&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; is setting this example.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The authorities, the bureaucrats, the politicians and responsible technicians have done all they could. We must acknowledge that.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;It is now up to us to prove that we can do even better and even more. Protests alone are of no help here.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Only a new society, respecting the true ecologically-creative values which we establish ourselves, can bring about gradual change.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In detail:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cold incineration (rotting in refuse dumps) has the same effects as hot incineration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same oxygen is consumed, i.e. removed from the air, simply over a longer period of time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The air is enriched with the same amount of CO2, over a longer period of time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;3.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Approximately the same toxins and pollutants escape into the air and water; it simply takes longer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;4.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same heat (energy) is produced, albeit unexploited. E.g., a piece of wood humifying and mineralizing over some 3-5 years releases the same energy as when burnt in an incinerator in just one minute.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;5.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same ash (residue) is produced from a piece of wood in one minute (hot incineration) as over 3-5 years of cold incineration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;However: In refuse dumps, toxins are not rendered harmless and escape unchecked. This applies particularly to heavy metals, which in Spittelau will be recovered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Should refuse have to be removed from the city by lorry, whether to a dump or an incineration plant, let us say 30 km outside Vienna, the exhaust fumes and toxic emissions from the lorries&rsquo; internal combustion engines would pose a much greater and real danger to the population than the Spittelau district heating station, and an additional one at that. Consider this: Some 2000 tons of refuse per day, transported in some 300 lorries, each lorry emitting some 5 times the toxic fumes, unfiltered as an ordinary car. And that in the street at breathing level! Nor could the refuse be employed for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&rsquo;s district heating system. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&rsquo;s already potentially dangerous refuse dumps are almost full and can take no more.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The earth&rsquo;s air layer is a communicating system. Whether a smokestack stands in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Alaska&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, the effects are virtually the same for all of earth&rsquo;s inhabitants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thus the deteriorating quality of our air can be confirmed anywhere in the world, whether in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Europe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Sahara&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; desert or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;New   Zealand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;. Our present ungraded refuse is so toxic that the compost obtained from it cannot even be used for gardening or agriculture. Horrifyingly, not even for forests.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;According to measurement and calculations, the level of dioxin emissions from the Spittelau stack will total less than 0,0000000004 (9 zeros) per m&sup3; air. The amount of dioxin or foran actually inhaled per m&sup3; air will be maximum 0,00000000000002 (13 zeros). I do not believe these figures to be fabricated. Even if they had fewer zeros, they would still be impressive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Proportional to the distance between earth and moon (380.000 km) the pollutant volume would cover a distance of 1,2 millimetres! Spittelau&rsquo;s future filtering capacity is quite incredible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In particular, up to 99 % of the toxic heavy metals cadmium, lead, zinc, chrome etc. will be filtered out and will reach neither our air nor our ground water.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The slag and flue dust produced will be rendered highly innocuous by the denox system and effectively fully neutralized. This is one of the most outstanding features of the new plant. Moreover, a large p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;art  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;of the slag is bound in glass. The heavy metals are recovered from the filters. The concentration of heavy metals in the filters is far higher than in mines. And their recovery is very much more simple and energy-efficient. High levels of heavy metal are recovered which would otherwise not only be lost but would also poison us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cigarette smoke and car exhausts are far more dangerous in terms of dioxins carbon monoxides, nitrogen monoxides and so on. Just how many (unfiltered) stacks that equals is unimaginable. And posing a very real hazard down here at breathing level!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Inhaling the exhaust fumes of a single car will kill a person in one minute. There are, I believe, 600.000 cars registered in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;! But still we all drive cars, even the environmentalists among us. What are the levels like here, I wonder? Still a point followed by several zeros?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The obstacles to an (exhaust-free) motorized society are similar to those facing a waste-free society.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Nothing can be achieved overnight. Before I decided to accept the commission, L&ouml;tsch helped me to formulate a letter of refusal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But he subsequently arrived at the opinion that obstructing the new incineration plant without supplying a realistic present alternative would cause greater ecological damage than its actual commissioning, and left the decision regarding its artistic refurbishing up to me. In-depth studies on a global basis reveal what I already knew. Refuse separation offers no long-term escape from the ecological impasse. Compostable, largely non-toxic substances would have to be allowed to decompose separately.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The only answer is total refuse avoidance by the entire human race: A wasteless society. And this total refuse avoidance could only be achieved thus: No fossil fuels, no noxious or radioactive materials to be extracted from the earth&rsquo;s upper crust and brought to the surface! Once materials such as oil, coal and toxic substances have been brought to the earth&rsquo;s surface, it makes no difference whether they are burnt or dumped in hot or cold incineration, whether they are turned into synthetic materials, plastic etc. or recycled, whether these plastic and other synthetic goods are incinerated or not incinerated, recycled or dumped.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The final result is always the same. An atmosphere unbalanced by excess toxic substances and a world of poisoned humus, water, air, plants, animals and people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thus if the enormous concentration of fossil fuels, formed over millions of years, is incinerated at once, either hot or cold, i.e. by dumping, or if the products of oil and coal are incinerated or not incinerated, the catastrophic result is the same, with inevitable consequences for the next generations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;There is only one way out. To extract no further fossil fuels from below ground as from now.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Nature has taken millions of years to cover the toxic substances originally composing the earth&rsquo;s surface with a layer of humus, vegetation and oxygen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;By returning these toxins to the earth&rsquo;s surface, we are violently recreating those original conditions of millions of years ago, when man could not yet live upon the earth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I hope you appreciate the problem in its entirety.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Immediate necessities demand that we choose not merely the lesser evil but the only possible current solution, and that we fight daily for a better future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In the spirit of fairness and in the interests of the ecological debate which affects us all, please publish this letter alongside your own in the &ldquo;Wiener Naturschutznachrichten&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cordially, Hundertwasser&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_contents_en-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;My dear friend Minich,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thank you for your letter of 25 May, RE the Spittelau district heating station.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I fully understand that you are against it, just like myself and many other concerned people. I personally grew up in the Brigittenau area, in other words very close by.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But your letter lacks a practical alternative for today.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We ourselves, all of us, every Viennese citizen, are responsible for our own refuse. If we produced no refuse, there would be none to burn. Let us boycott waste-incineration plants by simply not supplying them with refuse. Is that feasible in present-day &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;? Refuse should be made a criminal offence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Refuse producers, packaging industries, refuse causers, refuse makers, i.e. all of us, should be severely punished in order to induce a radical avoidance of waste.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I spent a year agonizing over the same arguments for declining the project as yours, before finally deciding to accept the commission for the visual redesign of the plant. As you know, I am vehemently against all environmental pollutants and have always used all my means to promote a waste-free society.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I am a realist, however.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We cannot close our eyes to reality.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;All my utopias and dreams can be realized, as I am continually demonstrating.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Having made a detailed study of what would happen if Spittelau did not go into operation, i.e. by thinking it through to the end, I decided the negative consequences are far worse.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;We won&rsquo;t have a waste-free society tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But hopefully the day after tomorrow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I will fight vehemently for it, and we must all work daily towards it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The negative points:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Refuse incineration in a built-up urban area with the fear that toxins will endanger people in the city.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Skipping the humus phase by incinerating.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The positive points:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Extensive, almost complete neutralization of toxic substances in refuse through incineration in new (state-of-the-art) denox filter plants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Heat extraction: It will heat 10-15 % of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;3.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Following my redesign the works will lose their ugliness, and thus the psychological distress caused by the earlier sight of its immense and visibly threatening pollution of the environment will be relieved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I am certain that people will even feel pride at having this new symbol of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; in their neighbourhood, and this will increase the self-confidence and joy in life of an entire city district. Particularly when the filter plant and technical section are setting examples to the world. However paradoxical it sounds, I see the Spittelau station as a first call for a more attractive, waste-free environment. I am also proud that &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Austria&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; is setting this example.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The authorities, the bureaucrats, the politicians and responsible technicians have done all they could. We must acknowledge that.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;It is now up to us to prove that we can do even better and even more. Protests alone are of no help here.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Only a new society, respecting the true ecologically-creative values which we establish ourselves, can bring about gradual change.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In detail:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cold incineration (rotting in refuse dumps) has the same effects as hot incineration:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;1.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same oxygen is consumed, i.e. removed from the air, simply over a longer period of time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;2.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The air is enriched with the same amount of CO2, over a longer period of time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;3.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Approximately the same toxins and pollutants escape into the air and water; it simply takes longer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;4.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same heat (energy) is produced, albeit unexploited. E.g., a piece of wood humifying and mineralizing over some 3-5 years releases the same energy as when burnt in an incinerator in just one minute.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;5.    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The same ash (residue) is produced from a piece of wood in one minute (hot incineration) as over 3-5 years of cold incineration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;However: In refuse dumps, toxins are not rendered harmless and escape unchecked. This applies particularly to heavy metals, which in Spittelau will be recovered.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Should refuse have to be removed from the city by lorry, whether to a dump or an incineration plant, let us say 30 km outside Vienna, the exhaust fumes and toxic emissions from the lorries&rsquo; internal combustion engines would pose a much greater and real danger to the population than the Spittelau district heating station, and an additional one at that. Consider this: Some 2000 tons of refuse per day, transported in some 300 lorries, each lorry emitting some 5 times the toxic fumes, unfiltered as an ordinary car. And that in the street at breathing level! Nor could the refuse be employed for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&rsquo;s district heating system. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;&rsquo;s already potentially dangerous refuse dumps are almost full and can take no more.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The earth&rsquo;s air layer is a communicating system. Whether a smokestack stands in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Alaska&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, the effects are virtually the same for all of earth&rsquo;s inhabitants.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thus the deteriorating quality of our air can be confirmed anywhere in the world, whether in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Europe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Sahara&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; desert or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;New   Zealand&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;. Our present ungraded refuse is so toxic that the compost obtained from it cannot even be used for gardening or agriculture. Horrifyingly, not even for forests.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;According to measurement and calculations, the level of dioxin emissions from the Spittelau stack will total less than 0,0000000004 (9 zeros) per m&sup3; air. The amount of dioxin or foran actually inhaled per m&sup3; air will be maximum 0,00000000000002 (13 zeros). I do not believe these figures to be fabricated. Even if they had fewer zeros, they would still be impressive.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Proportional to the distance between earth and moon (380.000 km) the pollutant volume would cover a distance of 1,2 millimetres! Spittelau&rsquo;s future filtering capacity is quite incredible.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In particular, up to 99 % of the toxic heavy metals cadmium, lead, zinc, chrome etc. will be filtered out and will reach neither our air nor our ground water.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The slag and flue dust produced will be rendered highly innocuous by the denox system and effectively fully neutralized. This is one of the most outstanding features of the new plant. Moreover, a large p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;art  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;of the slag is bound in glass. The heavy metals are recovered from the filters. The concentration of heavy metals in the filters is far higher than in mines. And their recovery is very much more simple and energy-efficient. High levels of heavy metal are recovered which would otherwise not only be lost but would also poison us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cigarette smoke and car exhausts are far more dangerous in terms of dioxins carbon monoxides, nitrogen monoxides and so on. Just how many (unfiltered) stacks that equals is unimaginable. And posing a very real hazard down here at breathing level!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Inhaling the exhaust fumes of a single car will kill a person in one minute. There are, I believe, 600.000 cars registered in &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Vienna&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;! But still we all drive cars, even the environmentalists among us. What are the levels like here, I wonder? Still a point followed by several zeros?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The obstacles to an (exhaust-free) motorized society are similar to those facing a waste-free society.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Nothing can be achieved overnight. Before I decided to accept the commission, L&ouml;tsch helped me to formulate a letter of refusal.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;But he subsequently arrived at the opinion that obstructing the new incineration plant without supplying a realistic present alternative would cause greater ecological damage than its actual commissioning, and left the decision regarding its artistic refurbishing up to me. In-depth studies on a global basis reveal what I already knew. Refuse separation offers no long-term escape from the ecological impasse. Compostable, largely non-toxic substances would have to be allowed to decompose separately.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The only answer is total refuse avoidance by the entire human race: A wasteless society. And this total refuse avoidance could only be achieved thus: No fossil fuels, no noxious or radioactive materials to be extracted from the earth&rsquo;s upper crust and brought to the surface! Once materials such as oil, coal and toxic substances have been brought to the earth&rsquo;s surface, it makes no difference whether they are burnt or dumped in hot or cold incineration, whether they are turned into synthetic materials, plastic etc. or recycled, whether these plastic and other synthetic goods are incinerated or not incinerated, recycled or dumped.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;The final result is always the same. An atmosphere unbalanced by excess toxic substances and a world of poisoned humus, water, air, plants, animals and people.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Thus if the enormous concentration of fossil fuels, formed over millions of years, is incinerated at once, either hot or cold, i.e. by dumping, or if the products of oil and coal are incinerated or not incinerated, the catastrophic result is the same, with inevitable consequences for the next generations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;There is only one way out. To extract no further fossil fuels from below ground as from now.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Nature has taken millions of years to cover the toxic substances originally composing the earth&rsquo;s surface with a layer of humus, vegetation and oxygen.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;By returning these toxins to the earth&rsquo;s surface, we are violently recreating those original conditions of millions of years ago, when man could not yet live upon the earth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;I hope you appreciate the problem in its entirety.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Immediate necessities demand that we choose not merely the lesser evil but the only possible current solution, and that we fight daily for a better future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;In the spirit of fairness and in the interests of the ecological debate which affects us all, please publish this letter alongside your own in the &ldquo;Wiener Naturschutznachrichten&rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cordially, Hundertwasser&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_contents_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Lieber Freund Minich, &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Dank f&uuml;r deinen Brief vom 25. Mai betreffs Fernheizwerk Spittelau. Ich verstehe v&ouml;llig, dass du dagegen bist, ebenso wie ich auch und viele besorgte Menschen. Ich selbst bin in der Brigittenau aufgewachsen, also ganz dicht dabei. Es fehlt in deinem Brief jedoch ein realisierbarer Alternativvorschlag f&uuml;r jetzt. &lt;em&gt;Wir selbst, wir alle, jeder einzelne Wiener, sind f&uuml;r unseren M&uuml;ll verantwortlich. Wenn wir keinen M&uuml;ll produzieren, kann keiner verbrannt werden. Boykottieren wir die M&uuml;llverbrennungsanlagen dadurch, dass wir ihr keinen M&uuml;ll liefern&lt;/em&gt;. Ist das in Wien zur Zeit realisierbar? Man m&uuml;sste den M&uuml;ll kriminalisieren.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Man m&uuml;sste die M&uuml;llerzeuger, die Verpackungsindustrie, die M&uuml;llverursacher, die M&uuml;llmacher, d.h. uns alle empfindlich bestrafen, um eine radikale M&uuml;llvermeidung zu erreichen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich habe ein ganzes Jahr mit mir gerungen, mit den gleichen Argumenten wie die deinen f&uuml;r eine Absage, ehe ich mich entschlossen habe, den Auftrag der architektonisch visuellen Neugestaltung anzunehmen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Wie du wei&szlig;t, bin ich vehement gegen alle Umweltgifte und trete seit immer mit allen meinen Mitteln f&uuml;r eine abfallfreie Gesellschaft ein.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich bin jedoch Realist. Man kann nicht die Augen vor der Realit&auml;t verschlie&szlig;en. Alle meine Utopien und Tr&auml;ume sind realisierbar, was ich auch immer wieder unter Beweis stelle.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Nach eingehender Pr&uuml;fung, was passieren w&uuml;rde, wenn Spittelau nicht in Betrieb geht, d.h. &lt;em&gt;wenn man zu Ende denkt&lt;/em&gt;, sind die negativen Auswirkungen bei weitem schlechter. Denn die abfallfreie Gesellschaft ist nicht f&uuml;r morgen. Hoffentlich f&uuml;r &uuml;bermorgen. Ich werde vehement daf&uuml;r k&auml;mpfen und wir alle m&uuml;ssen t&auml;glich daran arbeiten.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die negativen &Uuml;berlegungen:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;M&uuml;llverbrennung im verbauten Stadtgebiet mit der Furcht, dass      Giftstoffe innerhalb der Stadt Menschen gef&auml;hrden.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&Uuml;berspringung der Humusetappe durch die Verbrennung. Der      Recycling-Kreis wird unterbrochen.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die positiven &Uuml;berlegungen:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Weitgehende, fast vollst&auml;ndige Unsch&auml;dlichmachung der Giftstoffe      im M&uuml;ll durch Verbrennung mit neuer (letzter Stand) De Nox Filteranlage.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Gewinnung von W&auml;rme, 10 - 15 % Wiens wird damit geheizt.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Durch meine Neugestaltung wird dem Werk die H&auml;sslichkeit dieser      Gro&szlig;anlage genommen, wodurch die psychische Belastung durch die immense      und bedrohliche optische Umweltverschmutzung des bisherigen Anblickes      wegf&auml;llt.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEnvelopeReturn&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich bin sicher, es entsteht sogar ein Stolz, dieses neue Wahrzeichen Wiens in der N&auml;he zu haben und dies hebt das Selbstbewusstsein und die Lebensfreude eines ganzen Stadtteils. Insbesondere wenn auch die Filteranlage und der technische Teil weltweit beispielgebend sind.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;So paradox es klingt, ich sehe die Spittelauer Anlage als erstes Mahnmal f&uuml;r eine sch&ouml;nere abfallfreie Zukunft. Ich bin auch stolz, dass diese Beispielgebung in &Ouml;sterreich geschieht.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Obrigkeit, die B&uuml;rokratie, die Politiker und verantwortungsvolle Techniker haben getan, was sie konnten. Man muss das anerkennen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es liegt an uns zu beweisen, dass wir noch mehr und noch besser tun k&ouml;nnen. Proteste allein helfen hier nichts. Nur eine neue Gesellschaft, ausgerichtet nach den wahren &ouml;kologisch-kreativen Werten, die wir selbst schaffen, kann eine schrittweise Wende herbeif&uuml;hren.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Nun im Detail:&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die kalte Verbrennung (Verrottung in Deponien von M&uuml;ll) hat die gleiche Auswirkung wie die hei&szlig;e Verbrennung.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0cm&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es wird der gleiche Sauerstoff verbrannt, d.h. der Luft entnommen,      nur in einem gr&ouml;&szlig;eren Zeitraum.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Luft wird mit dem gleichen CO&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt; angereichert in      einem gr&ouml;&szlig;eren Zeitraum.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es entweichen in Luft und Wasser etwa die gleichen Gifte und      Schadstoffe, nur dauert es l&auml;nger.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es entsteht die gleiche W&auml;rme (Energie), allerdings ungen&uuml;tzt.      Z.B. ein St&uuml;ck Holz gibt die gleiche Energie ab bei der Humusierung und      Mineralisierung in etwa 3 - 5 Jahren wie im Ofen verbrannt in nur einer      Minute.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Es entsteht die gleiche Asche (R&uuml;ckstand). Ein St&uuml;ck Holz in einer      Minute (hei&szlig;e Verbrennung) oder in 3 - 5 Jahren bei der kalten Verbrennung&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Nur: Bei den Deponien werden die Gifte nicht unsch&auml;dlich gemacht und entweichen ungehindert. Insbesondere die Schwermetalle, die in Spittelau wiedergewonnen werden.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Falls der M&uuml;ll mit Lastwagen aus der Stadt gebracht wird, sei es auf eine Deponie, sei es in eine Verbrennungsanlage, sagen wir 30 km von Wien entfernt, w&uuml;rde allein durch den Rauchgas- und Giftaussto&szlig; der Verbrennungsmotoren der Lastwagen eine weit h&ouml;here und tats&auml;chliche Gef&auml;hrdung der Bev&ouml;lkerung eintreten als durch das Spittelauer Fernheizwerk und zwar zus&auml;tzlich. Man bedenke: etwa 2.000 Tonnen M&uuml;ll t&auml;glich, transportiert mit etwa 300 Lastwagen, mit je Lastwagen etwa 5-mal so viel Giftauspuff, ungefiltert, wie bei normalen Autos. Noch dazu auf den Stra&szlig;en in Atemh&ouml;he! Au&szlig;erdem k&ouml;nnte der M&uuml;ll nicht f&uuml;r das Fernw&auml;rmesystem Wiens genutzt werden. Die ohnehin potentiell gef&auml;hrlichen Deponien Wiens sind fast voll und k&ouml;nnen nichts mehr aufnehmen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Luftschicht der Erde ist ein kommunizierendes System. Ob der Schlot in Wien oder in Alaska steht, es hat eigentlich die gleiche Auswirkung f&uuml;r alle Erdbewohner. So wie die Verschlechterung der Atemluft weltweit konstatierbar ist, ob in Europa, in der W&uuml;ste Sahara oder in Neuseeland. &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Der jetzige unsortierte M&uuml;ll ist derartig giftig, dass der daraus gewonnene Kompost nicht mehr als Humus f&uuml;r Garten und Landwirtschaft verwendet werden kann. Erschreckenderweise auch nicht f&uuml;r W&auml;lder.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Nach Messungen und Berechnungen wird der anfallende Dioxingehalt, der aus dem Spittelauer Schlot herauskommen wird, pro m&sup3; Luft weniger als 0.0000000004 (9 Nullen) betragen. Der tats&auml;chlich eingeatmete Dioxin- bzw. Forangehalt pro m&sup3; Luft wird aber nur maximal 0.00000000000002 (13 Nullen) betragen. Ich glaube nicht, dass diese Zahlen erlogen sind. Auch weniger Nullen w&auml;ren beeindruckend. Die Schadstoffmenge w&auml;re, proportional auf die Entfernung Mond - Erde (380.000 km) &uuml;bertragen, die Strecke von 1,2 Millimetern!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die zuk&uuml;nftige Filterkapazit&auml;t von Spittelau ist schon unglaublich. Insbesondere werden auch die giftigen Schwermetalle Kadmium, Blei, Zink, Chrom etc. zu 99.9 % ausgefiltert und gelangen nicht in Luft oder Grundwasser.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die anfallende Schlacke und Flugasche wird bei dem Denox-System ganz besonders unsch&auml;dlich gemacht und quasi total neutralisiert. Das ist &uuml;berhaupt eine der ganz gro&szlig;en Errungenschaften der neuen Anlage. Au&szlig;erdem ist ein gro&szlig;er Teil der Schlacke in Glas gebunden.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Aus den Filtern werden die Schwermetalle wiedergewonnen. Die Konzentration der Schwermetalle in den Filtern ist weitaus h&ouml;her als in den Bergwerken und die R&uuml;ckgewinnung der Schwermetalle ist sehr viel einfacher und energiesparender. Man gewinnt hohe Mengen von Schwermetallen, die normalerweise nicht nur verloren gehen, sondern uns alle vergiften.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Zigarettenrauch und Autoabgase ergeben eine viel schlimmere Gef&auml;hrdung durch Dioxine, Kohlenmonoxyde, Stickoxyde und so fort. Wie viel Schlote (ungefiltert) das ausmacht, ist nicht auszudenken. Mit einer tats&auml;chlichen Gef&auml;hrdung von unten her, in Atemh&ouml;he!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Wenn man den Auspuff eines einzigen Autos einatmet ist man binnen Minuten tot. 600.000 Autos sind in Wien registriert, glaube ich! Trotzdem fahren wir alle Autos, auch die Umweltsch&uuml;tzer. Wie sind da die Giftzahlen? Auch eine Null mit vielen Nullen?&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Problematik einer Auto-(Abgas-)freien Gesellschaft ist &auml;hnlich der einer abfallfreien Gesellschaft. Es geht nicht von heute auf morgen. Bevor ich mich entschlossen habe, diesen Auftrag anzunehmen, hat mir L&ouml;tsch geholfen, einen Absagebrief zu konzipieren.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Dann war er jedoch auch der Meinung, dass eine Verhinderung der neuen Verbrennungsanlage mangels einer realistischen jetzigen Alternative &ouml;kologisch einen gr&ouml;&szlig;eren Schaden verursachen w&uuml;rde als die Inbetriebnahme und hat die Entscheidung der k&uuml;nstlerischen Umgestaltung mir &uuml;berlassen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Tiefergehende Studien auf globaler Basis bringen das, was ich ohnehin schon wusste. Eine M&uuml;lltrennung bringt nur eine tempor&auml;re Entsch&auml;rfung der &ouml;kologischen Sackgasse. Die kompostierbaren, weitgehend ungiftigen Substanzen m&uuml;ssten gesondert der Humusierung zug&auml;nglich gemacht werden.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Jedoch nur eine totale M&uuml;llvermeidung des gesamten Menschengeschlechtes w&auml;re die Antwort: eine abfalllose Gesellschaft.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Und diese totale M&uuml;llvermeidung w&auml;re nur die: keine brennbaren Fossilien, keine giftigen und radioaktiven Stoffe aus dem Untergrund der oberen Erdkruste an die Oberfl&auml;che bef&ouml;rdern! Wenn Stoffe wie Erd&ouml;l, Kohle und Giftsubstanzen an die Erdoberfl&auml;che gebracht worden sind, ist es ganz egal, ob man sie verbrennt oder deponiert, im hei&szlig;er oder kalter Verbrennung, ob man sie in Kunststoffe, Plastik etc. umwandelt, ob man sie wiederverwertet, ob man diese Plastik- oder sonstigen Kunststoffprodukte verbrennt oder nicht verbrennt, wiederverwertet oder deponiert. Das Endergebnis ist das gleiche. Eine mit Giftstoffen angereicherte und aus dem Gleichgewicht geratene Atmosph&auml;re, ein vergifteter Humus-, Wasser-, Luft-, Pflanzen-, Tier- und Menschenraum.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Also, wenn man die ungeheure Konzentration von fossilen Brennstoffen, die sich in Jahrmillionen gebildet haben, auf einmal verbrennt oder kalt verbrennt, d.h. deponiert, oder die Produkte aus &Ouml;l und Kohle verbrennt oder nicht verbrennt, das katastrophale Resultat ist das gleiche mit ausweglosen Konsequenzen f&uuml;r die n&auml;chsten Generationen. Es gibt nur einen Ausweg. Ab sofort keine fossilen Brennstoffe mehr aus dem Untergrund holen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Die Natur hat Jahrmillionen gebraucht, um die Gifte, die sich an der Oberfl&auml;che der Erde befanden, mit einer Humus-, Pflanzen- und Sauerstoffschichte zuzudecken. Indem wir diese Gifte wieder an die Oberfl&auml;che bef&ouml;rdern, erzeugen wir gewaltsam wieder den urspr&uuml;nglichen Zustand von vor Jahrmillionen, als der Mensch auf Erden noch nicht leben konnte.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ich hoffe, du siehst die ganze Problematik in ihrer Gesamtheit. Man muss f&uuml;r die sofortigen Notwendigkeiten nicht nur das kleinere &Uuml;bel, sondern den einzig m&ouml;glichen Ausweg zur Zeit w&auml;hlen und t&auml;glich f&uuml;r eine bessere Zukunft k&auml;mpfen.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Bitte diesen Antwortbrief fairerweise und im Interesse der uns alle betreffenden &ouml;kologischen Sache gleichzeitig mit deinem Brief in den Wiener Naturschutznachrichten zu ver&ouml;ffentlichen.&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_en-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Written in Vienna, 3 June 1988.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_occasion_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Geschrieben in Wien am 3. Juni 1988.&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_published_en-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Wiener &lt;em&gt;Naturschutz-Nachrichten&lt;/em&gt; 4/88, Vienna (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Rand, Harry: Friedensreich Hundertwasser. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Taschen: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Cologne&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, 1991, pp. 70-71, abridged edition 1993 and edition 2003, p. 60 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (ed.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;(Beautiful Paths &ndash; Thoughts on Art and Life) Langen M&uuml;ller: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;Munich&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial&quot;&gt;, 2004, pp. 268-272 (German)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
text_published_ge-'  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;Wiener &lt;em&gt;Naturschutz-Nachrichten&lt;/em&gt; 4/88, Wien&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoEndnoteText&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Rand, Harry: Friedensreich Hundertwasser. Taschen: K&ouml;ln 1991, S. 70-71, gek&uuml;rzte Ausgabe 1993 und Ausgabe 2003, S. 60&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Schurian, Walter (Hg.): Hundertwasser &ndash; Sch&ouml;ne Wege, Gedanken &uuml;ber Kunst und Leben. Langen M&uuml;ller Verlag: M&uuml;nchen 2004, S. 268-272&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;  ',
